{{vgname2|世嘉土星|ja=セガサターン|en=SEGA Saturn|多簡稱為'''SS'''、'''SAT'''}}，通稱'''土星'''，是[[日本|日本]][[電子遊戲發行商|電子遊戲商]][[世嘉|世嘉]]於1994年11月在日本、1995年5月在[[北美|北美]]、1995年7月在[[歐洲|歐洲]]發行的[[32位元|32位元]]次世代[[家用游戏机|家用遊戲機]]，前代主機為[[Mega_Drive|Mega Drive]]<ref name=":16">{{Cite web|url=https://sega.jp/history/hard/segasaturn/|script-title=ja:セガハード大百科 - セガサターン|accessdate=2018-08-13|work=セガハード大百科|publisher=SEGA|language=ja|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612163355/https://sega.jp/history/hard/segasaturn/|archivedate=2018-06-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":13">{{Cite web|url=https://sega.jp/history/hard/column/column_05.html|script-title=ja:セガードストーリー -  家庭用ゲーム機新時代の幕開け『セガサターン』|accessdate=2018-08-12|work=セガハード大百科|publisher=SEGA|language=ja|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612143740/https://sega.jp/history/hard/column/column_05.html|archivedate=2018-06-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。主機名「世嘉土星」源自於世嘉土星為世嘉發行的第六部主機，故取名為對應的[[太陽系|太陽系]]第六顆[[行星|行星]]——[[土星|土星]]<ref name=":16" />。繼任主機為[[Dreamcast|Dreamcast]]。

世嘉土星的開發始於1992年，當時世嘉甫推出劃時代的[[三维计算机图形|3D]][[街机主板|街機主板]]{{link-en|SEGA Model-1|SEGA Model-1}}。世嘉土星採用雙[[中央处理器|中央處理器]]架構，主機內含有兩顆日本[[日本電子工業|電子公司]][[日立製作所|日立]]製造的[[SuperH|SH-2]] [[32位元|32位元]][[精簡指令集|精簡指令集]]（RISC）處理器<ref name=":14">{{Cite web|url=https://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/data.html|script-title=ja:[セガハード大百科] セガサターン 各種データ|accessdate=2018-08-12|work=SEGA|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160814144719/http://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/data.html|archivedate=2016-08-14|dead-url=no|language=ja}}</ref>；世嘉土星原先在設計上只有一顆[[圖形處理器|圖形處理器]]VDP1，但為抗衡競爭對手[[索尼|索尼]]推出的家用遊戲機[[PlayStation|PlayStation]]而加入另一圖形處理器VDP2，使VDP1得以專注處理[[三维计算机图形|3D圖形]]運算<ref name=":13" />。

世嘉土星雖然在日本獲得成功，但是在北美地區的發售由於操之過急，導致[[游戏开发者|第三方遊戲開發商]]沒有時間為其開發遊戲，因此在3D運算技術更為先進、遊戲陣容更為豐富的PlayStation及[[任天堂64|任天堂64]]的影響下，世嘉土星之[[市場佔有率|市佔率]]不斷流失<ref name=":24" />；世嘉自家招牌遊戲《[[音速小子|音速小子]]》系列最新遊戲開發中止一事，也對世嘉土星造成不小的打擊<ref name="Edge X-Treme" />。最終世嘉土星於2000年全面停售，世嘉公司也因其後繼主機Dreamcast的失敗，而於隔年退出家用遊戲機硬體市場。世嘉土星在其生命週期中僅售出了926萬部<ref name="CESA" />，以商業角度來看是失敗的。

儘管有著《[[飛天幽夢|飛天幽夢]]》、《{{link-en|飛龍騎士|Panzer Dragoon}}》系列及《[[VR快打系列|VR快打]]》系列等優質遊戲，世嘉土星仍因其硬體架構過於複雜、第三方遊戲陣容不足及世嘉本身之商業決策錯誤而遭到抨擊。

== 歷史 ==
=== 背景 ===
[[Mega_Drive|Mega Drive]]（在北美地區被稱為SEGA Genesis）於1988年發售，銷售量達3075萬部，是世嘉歷年來最成功的主機<ref name="Retroinspection">{{Cite journal|title=Retroinspection: Mega Drive|author=Sczepaniak, John|url=http://www.sega-16.com/2006/09/retroinspection-mega-drive/|journal=[[Retro_Gamer|Retro Gamer]]|issue=27|year=2006|pages=42–47|accessdate=2018-08-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924100219/http://www.sega-16.com/2006/09/retroinspection-mega-drive/|archivedate=2015-09-24|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。1990年，時任日本[[世嘉|世嘉]]總裁兼執行長[[中山隼雄|中山隼雄]]提拔{{link-en|湯姆·卡林斯基|Tom Kalinske}}為美國世嘉總裁兼執行長。卡林斯基提出了四點計畫，以提升主機銷量：降低主機價格、加強廣告宣傳、美國在地化、將《[[音速小子_(1991年遊戲)|音速小子]]》[[同捆|同捆]]主機銷售<ref name="Eurogamer_CDSales">{{Cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-02-22-the-rise-and-fall-of-sega-enterprises|title=The Rise and Fall of Sega Enterprises|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2012-02-22|last=McFerran|first=Damien|work=Eurogamer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140216124431/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-02-22-the-rise-and-fall-of-sega-enterprises|archivedate=2014-02-16|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>{{sfn|Kent|2001|pp=424, 427}}。日本世嘉高層起初否決此計畫<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/gamespot/features/video/15influential/p13_01.html|title=Virtua Racing – Arcade (1992)|accessdate=2018-09-15|year=2001|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100412225953/http://www.gamespot.com/gamespot/features/video/15influential/p13_01.html|archivedate=2010-04-12|deadurl=yes}} cf. {{Cite web|url=https://www.wired.com/2012/09/how-virtua-fighter-saved-playstations-bacon/|title=How Virtua Fighter Saved PlayStation's Bacon|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2012-09-05|last=Feit|first=Daniel|work=[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141014093913/http://www.wired.com/2012/09/how-virtua-fighter-saved-playstations-bacon/|archivedate=2014-10-14|dead-url=no|language=en}} cf. {{Cite journal|title=The Man Behind the Legend|last=Thomason|first=Steve|date=2006-07|journal=[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]]|issue=205|volume=19|page=72|language=en}}</ref>{{sfn|Kent|2001|p=428}}，但中山隼雄認為計畫可行，並表示：「你是美國世嘉的總裁兼執行長，所以想做什麼就去做吧。」<ref name="Retroinspection" />結果計畫奏效，《[[音速小子_(1991年遊戲)|音速小子]]》叫好又叫座，主機在北美的銷售量甚至一度領先競爭對手[[超級任天堂|超級任天堂]]<ref name="Retroinspection32X">{{Cite journal|title=Retroinspection: Sega 32X|author=McFerran, Damien|journal=Retro Gamer|issue=77|year=2010|pages=44–49|language=en|quote='''Scot Bayless:''' The 32X call was made in early January [1994] ... There's a part of me that wishes the Saturn had adopted the 32X graphics strategy, but that ship had sailed long before the greenlight call from Nakayama.}}</ref><ref name="1UP VF">{{Cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/features/essential-50-virtua-fighter|title=The Essential 50 Part 35: Virtua Fighter|accessdate=2018-09-15|last=Leone|first=Matt|year=2010|work=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120719110526/http://www.1up.com/features/essential-50-virtua-fighter|archivedate=2012-07-19|deadurl=yes|language=en}}</ref>。不過，為其開發的配件[[Mega-CD|Mega-CD]]則銷量不佳<ref name="Eurogamer_CDSales" /><ref name="Retroinspection32X" />。

同時，世嘉也於[[街机|街機遊戲]]領域獲得成功。1992年，世嘉推出劃時代的[[街机主板|街機主板]]{{link-en|SEGA Model-1}}，並先後搭載由{{link-en|SEGA AM2|SEGA AM2}}部門開發的《{{link-en|VR賽車|Virtua Racing}}》及《[[VR战士_(游戏)|VR快打]]》，首度大規模運用[[三维计算机图形|3D多邊形]]技術<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":0" /><ref name="1UP VF" /><ref>{{Cite book|title=Replay: The History of Video Games|url=https://archive.org/details/replayhistoryofv0000dono|last=Donovan|first=Tristan|publisher=Yellow Ant|year=2010|isbn=978-0956507204|page=[https://archive.org/details/replayhistoryofv0000dono/page/267 267]|language=en|quote=One of the key objections to 3D graphics that developers had been raising with Sony was that while polygons worked fine for inanimate objects such as racing cars, 2D images were superior when it came to animating people or other characters. Virtua Fighter, Suzuki's follow-up to Virtua Racing, was a direct riposte to such thinking ... The characters may have resembled artists' mannequins but their lifelike movement turned Suzuki's game into a huge success that exploded claims that game characters couldn't be done successfully in 3D ... Teruhisa Tokunaka, chief executive officer of Sony Computer Entertainment, even went so far as to thank Sega for creating Virtua Fighter and transforming developers' attitudes.}}</ref>。《VR快打》不僅是第一款真正的3D[[格鬥遊戲|格鬥遊戲]]，還因其容易上手的操作方法及不同於傳統[[二维计算机图形|2D]]格鬥遊戲[[Combo_(电子游戏)|連擊系統]]的角色戰略系統設計而大受好評<ref name=":13" /><ref name="Edge VF">{{Cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/reviews/virtua-fighter-review/|title=Virtua Fighter Review|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=1994-12-22|work=Edge|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141210173015/http://www.edge-online.com/reviews/virtua-fighter-review/|archivedate=2014-12-10|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="NG February">{{Cite journal|title=Sega Saturn|date=1995-02|journal={{link-en|Next Generation}}|issue=2|volume=1|pages=36–43|quote=Sega's knee-jerk reaction was to delay its Saturn development program for a few months to incorporate a new video processor into the system. Not only would this boost its 2D abilities considerably (something that Sony's machine was less proficient at), but it would also provide better texture mapping for 3D graphics ... Of course, Hitachi's link with the Saturn project goes much deeper. In 1993, the Japanese electronics company set up a joint venture with Sega to develop a CPU for the Saturn based on proprietary Hitachi technology. Several Hitachi staff were seconded to Sega's Saturn division (it's now believed that the same team is now working on preliminary 64-bit technology for Sega), and the result was the SH-2 ... As with most Sega hardware, Model 1 was basically an expensive assortment of bought-in chips. Its main CPU, an {{link-en|NEC V60}} running at just 16 MHz, was simply too slow for the Saturn. And the bulk of Virtua Racing 's number crunching was handled by four serial DSPs that were way too costly to be included in any home system. Sega's consequent development of the SH-2 meant that it could also produce a Saturn-compatible arcade system.|language=en}}</ref>{{sfn|Mott|2013|pp=226, 250. "Virtua Racing ... was perhaps the first to treat polygons not as a graphical gimmick but as an opportunity to expand the boundaries of traditional driving games ... It's like witnessing the discovery of fire ... [Virtua Fighter] establish[ed] the template that future 3-D fighters would follow"}}{{sfn|Kent|2001|pp=501–502}}。世嘉也移植了部分街機遊戲至[[家用游戏机|家用遊戲機]]，如《VR賽車》（移植至[[Mega_Drive|Mega Drive]]）等<ref name="RetroinspectionSaturn">{{Cite journal|title=Retroinspection: Sega Saturn|author=McFerran, Damien|journal=Retro Gamer|issue=34|pages=44–49|language=en}}</ref>，最後促成了[[Super_32X|Super 32X]]配件的產生<ref name="RetroinspectionSaturn" /><ref name=":13" /><ref name="Retroinspection32X" />。

=== 開發 ===
世嘉土星的開發始於1992年。據時任世嘉專案經理岡村秀樹表示，主機名「世嘉土星」原先為主機之開發代號，其名取自於世嘉土星為世嘉發行的第六部主機，故取名為對應的[[太陽系|太陽系]]第六顆行星[[土星|土星]]，不過後來成為了主機正式名稱<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":13" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=EGM Interviews SEGA Saturn Product Manager Hideki Okamura|author=EGM|url=|date=1994-07|journal={{link-en|EGM2}}|issue=1|doi=|others=|year=|volume=1|page=114|pmid=|quote='''Hideki Okamura:''' [Saturn] was just a development code name for hardware that was adopted by the Japanese development staff. The name has become common knowledge and it has a nice ring to it.|language=en}}</ref><ref name=":10">{{Cite web|title=被時代所遺忘的另一個二十周年 一同回顧 SEGA Saturn 主機的獨特魅力！|url=https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/7/108357.html|work=巴哈姆特電玩資訊站|accessdate=2019-04-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150711131922/http://gnn.gamer.com.tw/7/108357.html|archivedate=2015-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1993年，世嘉與日本[[日本電子工業|電子公司]][[日立製作所|日立]]合作，為世嘉土星開發全新的[[中央處理器|中央處理器]]，即為後來的[[SuperH|SH-2]][[精簡指令集|精簡指令集]]（RISC）處理器<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":13" /><ref name="NG February" /><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1993/09/22/business/company-news-sega-to-use-hitachi-chip-in-video-game-machine.html|title=Sega to Use Hitachi Chip In Video Game Machine|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=1993-09-22|last=Pollack|first=Andrew|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140418061414/http://www.nytimes.com/1993/09/22/business/company-news-sega-to-use-hitachi-chip-in-video-game-machine.html|archivedate=2014-04-18|dead-url=no}} cf. {{Cite journal|title=Sega to add 64-Bit Processor to New Saturn System!|date=1993-12|journal=Electronic Gaming Monthly|issue=53|volume=5|page=68|quote=There are reportedly seven different processors in the Saturn. The main processor will be a custom 32-Bit RISC chip under joint development by Sega and Hitachi.}}</ref>。世嘉土星採用了罕見的雙處理器架構，據時任世嘉土星概念企劃人濱田和宏表示：「我們之所以會選用日立的SH-2，是因為其高效能及低成本。SH-2擁有類似於[[數位訊號處理器|數位訊號處理器]]（DSP）的演算架構，不過後來我們發現單一晶片的效能無法達到對3D運算的要求。」<ref name="NG February" /><ref name="NextGenDec">{{Cite journal|title=NG Hardware: Saturn|date=1995-12|journal=Next Generation|issue=12|volume=1|pages=45–48|quote=The early pictures and technical breakdowns have remained relatively close to the final system, perhaps because the system was completed far earlier than many people realize ... It was too late to make major alterations to the system, so, at the cost of pushing the launch schedule slightly, a video processor was added to the board to boost its 2D and 3D texture-mapping abilities. The real processing power of the Saturn comes from two Hitachi SH2 32-bit RISC processors running at 28 MHz. These processors were specially commissioned by Sega and are optimized for fast 3D graphics work.|language=en}}</ref>世嘉土星的設計於1993年底大致完成，不過在聽聞競爭對手[[索尼互動娛樂|索尼]]即將推出的全新家用遊戲機[[PlayStation_(遊戲機)|PlayStation]]擁有的3D運算能力後，世嘉決定為世嘉土星再加入一個[[圖形處理器|圖形處理器]]（即VDP2），使VDP1得以專注處理[[三维计算机图形|3D圖形]]運算<ref name=":13" /><ref name="NG February" /><ref name="NextGenDec" /><ref name="NG January">{{Cite journal|title=NG Hardware: Saturn|date=1995-01|journal=Next Generation|issue=1|volume=1|pages=44–45|quote=Sega has spent the last nine months or so playing catch-up with Sony after a publisher-friend tipped Sega off about the power of PlayStation.|language=en}}</ref>。原先世嘉打算同時發行採用[[CD-ROM|CD-ROM]]及採用[[ROM卡带|ROM卡帶]]兩種版本的主機，不過由於卡帶遊戲成本過高、儲存空間不足而放棄了卡帶版本<ref name="NG February" />。

世嘉土星的架構引發世嘉高層論戰。據湯姆·卡林斯基表示，美國世嘉對世嘉土星採用雙[[中央处理器|中央處理器]]及[[圖形處理器|圖形處理器]]的架構頗有微詞，「不斷反對決議」<ref name="1UP Pleasure and Pain">{{Cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/features/pleasure-pain?pager.offset=0|title=Sega Saturn: The Pleasure And The Pain|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2005-08-05|last=Sewart|first=Greg|work=1UP.com|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140317211403/http://www.1up.com/features/pleasure-pain?pager.offset=0|archivedate=2014-03-17|deadurl=yes|language=en}}</ref>。不過，卡林斯基仍在公開場合為世嘉土星的設計辯護：「我們期望將街機遊戲帶到家用遊戲機上，並試圖開發足以實現願景的架構，成果即是雙處理器設計。」<ref name="1UP Pleasure and Pain" /><ref name="Next Gen 8">{{Cite journal|title=Sega Saturn: You've Watched the TV Commercials...Now Read the Facts|date=1995-08|journal=Next Generation|issue=8|volume=1|pages=26–32|language=en}}</ref>卡林斯基曾企圖找尋其他圖形處理器替代品，並與[[視算科技|視算科技]]締結合作協議，不過最後遭世嘉總部駁回<ref name="IGNHistory_pg6">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/04/21/ign-presents-the-history-of-sega?page=6|title=IGN Presents the History of Sega|accessdate=2018-09-15|author=Fahs, Travis|date=2009-04-21|work=IGN|page=6|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140306162629/http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/04/21/ign-presents-the-history-of-sega?page=6|archivedate=2014-03-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Tale of Two E3s">{{Cite web|url=http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/tale-of-two-e3s-xbox-vs-sony-vs-sega/0118482|title=A Tale of Two E3s – Xbox vs Sony vs Sega|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2013-07-07|language=en|last=Dring|first=Christopher|work=MCVUK.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023102254/http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/tale-of-two-e3s-xbox-vs-sony-vs-sega/0118482|archivedate=2014-10-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>，視算科技則改與任天堂合作開發其次世代主機，即後來的[[任天堂64|任天堂64]]<ref name="IGNHistory_pg6" /><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/10/24/32x-follies|title=32X Follies|accessdate=2018-09-15|author=Buchanan, Levi|date=2008-10-24|work=IGN|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417080118/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/10/24/32x-follies|archivedate=2016-04-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。卡林斯基還曾一度與日本索尼電子出版的{{link-en|歐拉夫·歐拉弗森|Ólafur Jóhann Ólafsson}}及美國[[索尼|索尼]]的米基·舒爾霍夫（Micky Schulhof）計畫開發「世嘉/索尼聯合主機」，但是由於雙方對硬體的考量分歧而破局<ref name="Tale of Two E3s" /><ref name="Sega-16 Kalinske">{{Cite web|url=http://www.sega-16.com/feature_page.php?id=214&title=Interview%3A+Tom+Kalinske|title=Interview: Tom Kalinske|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2006-07-11|last=Horowitz|first=Ken|work=Sega-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090207173139/http://www.sega-16.com/feature_page.php?id=214&title=Interview%3A%20Tom%20Kalinske|archivedate=2009-02-07|language=en|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name=":4">{{Cite journal|title=Japanese Stats Give Saturn the Edge|date=1995-04|journal=Edge|issue=19|volume=3|pages=10–11|quote=This equates to the Saturn shifting an average number of 17,241 units a day and the PlayStation 15,789.|language=en}}</ref>。

1993年，日本世嘉調整內部人員組織，希望為世嘉土星的發售做好準備。為了確保世嘉土星擁有高品質的3D遊戲，日本世嘉將部分街機部門人員轉為負責開發家用遊戲機遊戲。許多部門於此時成立，如開發《[[铁甲飞龙|飛龍騎士]]》的{{link-en|AM6|SEGA AM6}}部門<ref name="Making of Panzer Dragoon">{{Cite web|url=http://www.nowgamer.com/features/894677/the_making_of_panzer_dragoon_saga_part_1.html|title=The Making Of ... Panzer Dragoon Saga Part 1|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2008-12-17|work=Now Gamer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724042310/http://www.nowgamer.com/features/894677/the_making_of_panzer_dragoon_saga_part_1.html|archivedate=2014-07-24|quote='''Kentaro Yoshida:''' We thought we'd have no problem making games that were superior to PlayStation games.|deadurl=yes|language=en}}</ref>。

1994年初，世嘉開始為Mega Drive開發新配件，名為[[Super_32X|Super 32X]]，使玩家能以較低的價格體驗[[32位元|32位元]]電子遊戲。此決議由中山隼雄提出，並受到美國世嘉高層的支持<ref name=":13" /><ref name="Retroinspection32X" />。據時任美國世嘉開發人員斯卡特·貝利斯（Scot Bayless）表示，中山隼雄擔心若世嘉土星的發售日期過晚，使硬體發售出現空窗期，可能使世嘉的市占率遭到[[雅達利|雅達利]]當時甫推出的[[雅達利Jaguar|雅達利Jaguar]]侵蝕<ref name=":13" /><ref name="Retroinspection32X" />。不過後來世嘉土星的開發時程符合進度，因此，美國世嘉決定在推出世嘉土星的同時，讓Super 32X作為配件，同時也是32位元主機的入門款發售<ref name="Retroinspection32X" /><ref name="Allgame32X">{{Cite web|url=http://allgame.com/platform.php?id=35|title=Sega Genesis 32X – Overview|accessdate=2018-09-15|author=Beuscher, David|work=Allgame|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141210012639/http://allgame.com/platform.php?id=35|archivedate=2014-12-10|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。據時任美國世嘉研發部門負責人喬·米勒（Joe Miller）表示，由於32X的硬體架構大致與世嘉土星相同，研發32X能使開發人員熟悉世嘉土星的硬體架構<ref name="Miller">{{Cite web|url=http://www.sega-16.com/2013/02/interview-joe-miller/|title=Interview: Joe Miller|accessdate=2018-09-15|author=Horowitz, Ken|date=2013-02-07|work=Sega-16|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202233248/http://www.sega-16.com/2013/02/interview-joe-miller/|archivedate=2013-12-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/making-playstation/3/|title=The Making Of: PlayStation|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2009-04-24|work=Edge|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018182151/http://www.edge-online.com/features/making-playstation/3/|archivedate=2014-10-18|page=3|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。分別由日本及美國主導的兩部主機於同一時間研發及發行的情況，使得當時的日本世嘉總部及美國世嘉情況緊張<ref name=":13" /><ref name="Retroinspection32X" />。

=== 發售 ===
[[File:Sega-Saturn-JP-Mk1-Console-Set.png|替代=]]
1994年11月22日，世嘉土星於日本首發，售價為44800[[日圓|日圓]]<ref name=":13" /><ref name="セガハード大百科">{{Cite web|url=https://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/|script-title=ja:[セガハード大百科] セガサターン|accessdate=2018-08-08|work=SEGA|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180630162450/https://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/|archivedate=2018-06-30|dead-url=no|language=ja}}</ref><ref name="#1">{{Cite web|title=被時代所遺忘的另一個二十周年 一同回顧 SEGA Saturn 主機的獨特魅力！|url=https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/7/108357.html|work=巴哈姆特電玩資訊站|accessdate=2019-04-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150711131922/http://gnn.gamer.com.tw/7/108357.html|archivedate=2015-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[VR战士_(游戏)|VR快打]]》移植版作為世嘉土星的首發遊戲，於發售初期銷量幾乎與主機不相上下，間接促成主機在日本的成功<ref name="Edge VF" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name="Edge Japanese launch">{{Cite journal|title=Sega and Sony Sell the Dream|date= 1995-02|journal=[[Edge_(magazine)|Edge]]|issue=17|volume=3|pages=6–9|quote=The December 3 ship-out of 100,000 PlayStations to stores across Japan ... was not met with the same euphoria-charged reception that the Saturn received ... Saturn arrived to a rapturous reception in Japan on November 22. 200,000 units sold out instantly on day one ... Japanese gamers were beside themselves as they walked away with their prized possession and a near-perfect conversion of the Virtua Fighter coin-op ... Sega (and Sony) have proved that with dedicated processors handling the drive (the SH-1 in the Saturn's case), negligible access times are possible.|language=en}}</ref>。由於《VR快打》的成功，日本世嘉預先準備的20萬部世嘉土星庫存銷售一空<ref name="IGNHistory_pg6" /><ref name="Edge Japanese launch" /><ref name=":5">{{Cite web|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/sega-profits-plunge-as-rivals-turn-up-the-heat-1581404.html|title=Sega profits plunge as rivals turn up the heat|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=1995-11-11|language=en|last=Horsman|first=Mathew|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150120053343/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/sega-profits-plunge-as-rivals-turn-up-the-heat-1581404.html|archivedate=2015-01-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。至1994年底，世嘉土星銷售量達50萬部，超越[[PlayStation_(遊戲機)|PlayStation]]的30萬部<ref name=":4" /><ref name=":6">{{Cite web|url=http://scei.co.jp/corporate/data/bizdataeu_e.html|title=Sony Computer Entertainment Inc. Business Development/Europe|accessdate=2018-09-15|publisher=Sony Computer Entertainment|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728173744/http://scei.co.jp/corporate/data/bizdataeu_e.html|language=en|archivedate=2014-07-28|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，並於1995年中達到一百萬部銷量<ref name=":13" /><ref name="Next Gen 8" />。[[Super_32X|Super 32X]]則於1994年11月發售，售價為世嘉土星的一半<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sega.jp/fb/segahard/32x/|script-title=ja:[セガハード大百科] スーパー３２Ｘ|accessdate=2018-08-08|work=SEGA|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140716105656/http://sega.jp/fb/segahard/32x/|archivedate=2014-07-16|dead-url=no|language=ja}}</ref>。不過，32X的銷量在聖誕節旺季後即一蹶不振<ref name=":13" /><ref name="Retroinspection32X" /><ref name="Allgame32X" />。雖然世嘉一度領先，但是索尼以低廉的授權費用、優質的開發工具及更有彈性的銷售節奏，吸引了大量第三方廠商，使PlayStation的市佔率逐漸超越世嘉土星<ref name=":3" /><ref name="IGN History of PlayStation">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/1998/08/28/history-of-the-playstation|title=History of the PlayStation|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120218120358/http://psx.ign.com/articles/060/060188p1.html|archivedate=2012-02-18|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref><ref name=":7">{{Cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2013/10/30/which-game-console-had-the-best-launch-lineup.aspx?PostPageIndex=3|title=Which Game Console Had The Best Launch Lineup?|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2013-10-30|last=Kato|first=Matthew|work=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]|page=3|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170630042313/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2013/10/30/which-game-console-had-the-best-launch-lineup.aspx?PostPageIndex=3|archivedate=2017-06-30|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。

1995年3月，美國世嘉宣布世嘉土星將於該年9月2日星期六（即日本的[[土曜日|土曜日]]）發售<ref name="Saturnday/1:12">{{Cite journal|title=Let the games begin: Sega Saturn hits retail shelves across the nation Sept. 2; Japanese sales already put Sega on top of the charts.|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Let+the+games+begin%3a+Sega+Saturn+hits+retail+shelves+across+the...-a016634009|date=1995-03-09|journal=[[Business_Wire|Business Wire]]|accessdate=2018-09-15|author=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025012132/http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Let+the+games+begin%3a+Sega+Saturn+hits+retail+shelves+across+the...-a016634009|archivedate=2014-10-25|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref><ref name=":8">{{Cite journal|title=Daytona USA|date=1995-06|journal=Edge|issue=21|volume=3|pages=72–5|quote=Although AM2 has managed to replicate the coin-op tolerably well, Saturn Daytona fails to capture the arcade experience that PlayStation Ridge Racer so convincingly delivers.|language=en}} cf. {{Cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/sep95/rracer.html|title=Prepare Yourself for the Ultimate Racing Experience|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=1995-09|last=McNamara|first=Andy|work=Game Informer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19971120013114/http://www.gameinformer.com/sep95/rracer.html|archivedate=1997-11-20|language=en|dead-url=yes}} cf. {{Cite journal|title=Pro Review: Daytona USA|author=Air Hendrix|date=1995-08|journal=GamePro|issue=73|volume=7|page=50|quote=Daytona pales in comparison to Ridge Racer for the Japanese PlayStation, which takes an early lead with better features, gameplay, and graphics.|language=en}}</ref>。不過，世嘉總部為與索尼抗衡，決議提早發售主機<ref name="Fight Club">{{Cite journal|title=Virtua Fight Club|author=Tokyo Drifter|date=2002-04|journal=GamePro|issue=163|volume=14|pages=48–50|language=en}}</ref>。1995年5月11日，第一屆[[E3电子娱乐展|E3]]於[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]舉辦。卡林斯基於發佈會中介紹世嘉土星，宣布其售價為399[[美元|美元]]，並與《[[VR战士_(游戏)|VR快打]]》同捆<ref name="Six launch">{{Cite web|url=https://www.thefreelibrary.com/Sega+Saturn+launch+takes+consumers+and+retailers+by+storm%3B+retailers...-a016867843|title=Sega Saturn launch takes consumers and retailers by storm; retailers struggling to keep up with consumer demand|accessdate=2018-09-15|language=en|date=1995-05-19|work=Business Wire|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161025111725/https://www.thefreelibrary.com/Sega+Saturn+launch+takes+consumers+and+retailers+by+storm%3B+retailers...-a016867843|archivedate=2016-10-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然後卡林斯基便突然表示，由於「消費者高度的期待及需求」<ref name="This Day">{{Cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/news/day-history-sega-announces-surprise|title=This Day in History: Sega Announces Surprise Saturn Launch|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2010-05-11|last=Cifaldi|first=Frank|work=1UP.com|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130629122913/http://www.1up.com/news/day-history-sega-announces-surprise|archivedate=2013-06-29|deadurl=yes|language=en}}</ref>，世嘉已準備鋪貨3萬部世嘉土星至[[玩具反斗城|玩具反斗城]]、[[GameStop|Babbage's]]、{{link-en|電子精品|EB Games}}及{{link-en|Software Etc.|B. Dalton}}等零售商<ref name="UK 7">{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/index.php?title=File:CVG_UK_164.pdf&page=7|title=CVG UK 164.pdf - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-13|work=SEGA Retro|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806121818/http://segaretro.org/index.php?title=File:CVG_UK_164.pdf&page=7|archivedate=2017-08-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":8" />。其他零售商如[[沃爾瑪|沃爾瑪]]及[[百思買|百思買]]因為未在名單中而不滿<ref name="Tale of Two E3s" /><ref name="Schilling">{{Cite journal|title=Technological Leapfrogging: Lessons From the U.S. Video Game Console Industry|last=Schilling|first=Mellissa A.|date=2003|journal=California Management Review|volume=45|pages=12, 23|quote=Lack of distribution may have contributed significantly to the failure of the Sega Saturn to gain an installed base. Sega had limited distribution for its Saturn launch, which may have slowed the building of its installed base both directly (because consumers had limited access to the product) and indirectly (because distributors that were initially denied product may have been reluctant to promote the product after the limitations were lifted). Nintendo, by contrast, had unlimited distribution for its Nintendo 64 launch, and Sony not only had unlimited distribution, but had extensive experience with negotiating with retailing giants such as Wal-Mart for its consumer electronics products.|number=3|language=en}} cf. {{Cite journal|title=Is War hell for Sega?|date=1996-01|journal=Next Generation|issue=13|volume=2|page=7|quote='''Tom Kalinske:''' We needed to do something shocking because we were $100 more than the other guy ... I still think [the surprise launch] was a good idea. If I had it to do over again would I do it a little differently? Yeah, definitely. I wouldn't take the risk of annoying retailers the way we did. I would clue them in and do an early launch in a region or three regions or something so we could include everybody.|language=en}}</ref>，[[KB_Toys|KB Toys]]甚至隨後將世嘉產品自其銷售列表中刪除<ref name=":8" />。之後[[索尼互動娛樂|索尼]]在宣布其主機PlayStation的價格時，其執行長史提夫·賴斯（Steve Race）僅說了一句話：「299美元。」即下台，現場掌聲不斷<ref name="Tale of Two E3s" />{{sfn|Harris|2014|p=545}}{{sfn|Kent|2001|pages=505, 516}}。在歐洲，世嘉土星也比原本的預定日期提前，於1995年7月8日發售，售價為399.99[[英鎊|英鎊]]<ref name="UK 30">{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/index.php?title=File:CVG_UK_165.pdf&page=30|title=CVG UK 165.pdf - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-13|work=SEGA Retro|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806233026/http://segaretro.org/index.php?title=File:CVG_UK_165.pdf&page=30|archivedate=2017-08-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="RetroinspectionSaturn" />。由於發售時間出乎意料，歐洲地區的零售商和媒體沒有時間用於宣傳，因此打擊了世嘉土星的銷量<ref name="Dear Saturn">{{Cite news|title=Dear Saturn Mag, I've Heard the Saturn Couldn't Handle Alex Kidd... Is This True?|date= 1995-12|work={{link-en|Sega Saturn Magazine}}|issue=2|volume=1|page=51|language=en}}</ref>。在PlayStation於9月發售後，其銷量立刻超越了世嘉土星<ref name=":5" /><ref name=":6" />。

美國世嘉花費了超過5億美元的費用，於包括[[電視廣告|電視廣告]]及《[[連線|連線]]》、《[[花花公子|花花公子]]》等[[雜誌|平面雜誌]]上宣傳世嘉土星<ref name="Next Gen 8" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Sega+Saturn+gets+astronomical+send+off+with+landmark+marketing...-a016940474|title=Sega Saturn gets astronomical send off with landmark marketing campaign; Sega breaks $50-million marketing campaign to support surprise launch at E3.|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=1995-05-11|work=Business Wire|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150218104132/http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Sega+Saturn+gets+astronomical+send+off+with+landmark+marketing...-a016940474|archivedate=2015-02-18|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref><ref name="Finn">{{Cite book|title=Computer Games and Digital Cultures: Conference Proceedings: Proceedings of the Computer Games and Digital Cultures Conference, June 6–8, 2002, Tampere, Finland|first1=Frans (editor)|last2=Finn|first2=Mark|publisher=Tampere University Press|year=2002|isbn=9789514453717|pages=45–58|chapter=Console Games in the Age of Convergence|last1=Mäyrä|language=en}}</ref>。與前代主機SEGA Genesis的廣告相比，世嘉土星的廣告更加注重成年及專業玩家<ref>{{Cite magazine|last=|first=|title=Sega: Who Do they Think you Are?|magazine={{link-en|Next Generation}}|issue=14|publisher={{link-en|Imagine Media}}|date=1996-02|page=71|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite magazine|last=|first=|title=Sega TV: Turn On, Tune In, Buy Hardware|magazine={{link-en|Next Generation}}|issue=14|publisher={{link-en|Imagine Media}}|date=1996-02|page=74|language=en}}</ref>。由於提早發售，世嘉土星的北美首發遊戲只有《VR快打》等6款，全部由世嘉自家製作，大多數的第三方遊戲都預計在世嘉土星原本的上市日期，即9月初時發行<ref name=":7" /><ref name="Six launch" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=1995: The Calm Before the Storm?|last=|first=|date=1996-01|journal={{link-en|Next Generation}}|publisher={{link-en|Imagine Media}}|issue=13|page=47|language=en}}</ref>。由於《VR快打》在北美人氣不高，再加上遊戲發行周期過長，抵銷了世嘉土星提早上市所帶來的好處<ref name="1UP Pleasure and Pain"/><ref name="IGNHistory_pg6" /><ref name="Innovation and competition2">{{Cite journal|title=Innovation and Competition in Standard-Based Industries: A Historical Analysis of the U.S. Home Video Game Market|first1=Scott|last2=Park|first2=Seung Ho|date=2002-02|journal=[[Institute_of_Electrical_and_Electronics_Engineers|IEEE]] Transactions on Engineering Management|volume=49|pages=67–82|last1=Gallagher|number=1}}</ref>。在PlayStation於9月發售後，其銷量立刻超越了世嘉土星五個月的銷售總和，第一波的10萬部庫存全數完售<ref name="IGN History of PlayStation" /><ref name="M2 Press">{{Cite news|url=http://www.m2.com/m2/web/story.php/1996852568440080DDE88025683B005E7A3F|title=Sega of America appoints Shoichiro Irimajiri chairman/chief executive officer|date=1996-07-16|accessdate=2018-09-17|quote=Sega of America Inc. (SOA) Monday announced that Shoichiro Irimajiri has been appointed chairman and chief executive officer. Sega also announced that Bernard Stolar, previously of Sony Computer Entertainment America, has joined the company as executive vice president, responsible for product development and third-party business ... Sega also announced that Hayao Nakayama and David Rosen have resigned as chairman and co-chairman of Sega of America, respectively.|journal=M2PressWIRE|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018032603/http://www.m2.com/m2/web/story.php/1996852568440080DDE88025683B005E7A3F|archivedate=2014-10-18|dead-url=no|language=en}}{{closed access}} {{subscription required|s}}</ref>。

PlayStation初期的成功主要歸於由[[南梦宫|南夢宮]]推出的《[[實感賽車|實感賽車]]》街機移植版<ref name=":6" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/a-history-of-videogame-hardware-sony-playstation/|title=A History of Videogame Hardware: Sony PlayStation|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2014-06-19|last=Parkin|first=Simon|work=Edge|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129042841/http://www.edge-online.com/features/a-history-of-videogame-hardware-sony-playstation/|archivedate=2014-11-29|deadurl=yes|language=en}}</ref>。相較於世嘉的《[[DaytonaUSA|Daytona USA]]》街機移植版，《實感賽車》的移植品質高出許多<ref name=":8" /><ref name="Irimajiri Settles In At Sega">{{Cite web|url=http://www.next-generation.com/news/072596b.html|title=Irimajiri Settles In At Sega|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=1996-07-25|work=Next Generation|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19961220195722/http://www.next-generation.com/news/072596b.html|archivedate=1996-12-20|language=en|deadurl=yes}} cf. {{Cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/jan96/rally.html|title=Easy Left, Baby|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=1996-01|last=Reiner|first=Andrew|work=Game Informer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19971120011601/http://www.gameinformer.com/jan96/rally.html|archivedate=1997-11-20|deadurl=yes}} cf. {{Cite journal|title=Top Gear|date=1996-02|journal=Next Generation|issue=14|volume=2|page=160|language=en}}</ref>。身為在街機市場的最大競爭對手<ref name="1UP VF" /><ref name="Johnston">{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/stolar-talks-dreamcast/1100-2464369/|title=Stolar Talks Dreamcast|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=1998-07-15|last=Johnston|first=Chris|work=GameSpot|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170710051328/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/stolar-talks-dreamcast/1100-2464369/|archivedate=2017-07-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，南夢宮同時也依據PlayStation的硬體架構，推出[[街机主板|街機主板]]{{link-en|Namco System 11}}<ref name="Cheap">{{Cite journal|title=Tekken|date= 1995-06|journal=Edge|issue=21|volume=3|pages=66–70|quote=Namco took a significant risk in basing its Tekken coin-op on raw PlayStation hardware, considering that it would be competing directly with Sega's Model 2-powered Virtua Fighter 2 ... For once, a home system can boast an identical conversion of a cutting-edge coin-op ... Namco's research section managing director, Shegeichi Nakamura ... explains: "When Sony came along we decided to go for a low-cost system—in short, we've left the big arcade stores to Sega and VF2 and Tekken has been sold to smaller arcade centres" ... Namco has a further four titles planned for System 11, all of which are likely to make the jump to the PlayStation.|language=en}}</ref>。儘管在技術上不如世嘉的{{link-en|SEGA Model-2}}，但是其較Model-2低廉的成本吸引了大量小型街機商<ref name="Fight Club" /><ref name="Cheap" />。1994年，南夢宮挖角了大量《VR快打》的開發人員後，推出3D格鬥遊戲《[[铁拳_(游戏)|鐵拳]]》。在前《VR快打》的設計者石井精一的主導下，《鐵拳》在各方面都超越了《VR快打》，幀率為《VR快打》的兩倍、[[材质贴图|貼圖]]也更細緻<ref name="NG">{{Cite journal|title=Namco|date= 1995-01|journal=Next Generation|issue=1|volume=1|pages=70–73|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Tekken|date=1995-02|journal=Next Generation|issue=2|volume=1|page=82|language=en}}</ref><ref name="Harada">{{Cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/an-audience-with-katsuhiro-harada/|title=An Audience With: Katsuhiro Harada – on 20 years of Tekken and the future of fighting games|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2013-09-23|language=en|work=[[Edge_(magazine)|Edge]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129114830/http://www.edge-online.com/features/an-audience-with-katsuhiro-harada/|archivedate=2014-11-29|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。Playstation版本的《鐵拳》近乎完美的移植了街機原作，並成為首款銷量超過一百萬的PlayStation遊戲<ref name="Fight Club" /><ref>cf. {{Cite journal|title=Pro Review: Virtua Fighter|author=Scary Larry|date=1995-08|journal=GamePro|issue=73|volume=7|page=48|quote=The graphics were state-of-the-art when this game was released in the arcades a year ago. Other fighters—notably Tekken and {{link-en|Toh Shin Den|Battle Arena Toshinden}}—now make better use of the polygon engine.}}</ref><ref name="IGN Shenmue">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/1999/07/14/shenmue-the-history|title=Shenmue, the History: Our look at Shenmue's history begins back in 1996|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=1999-07-13|work=IGN|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141030003504/http://www.ign.com/articles/1999/07/14/shenmue-the-history|archivedate=2014-10-30|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。1995年10月，世嘉將世嘉土星的售價降為299美元<ref name=":9">{{Cite journal|title=Sega announces $299 Sega Saturn core pack; "Virtua Fighter Remix" pack-in available for $349.|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Sega+announces+%24299+Sega+Saturn+core+pack%3b+%27%27Virtua+Fighter+Remix%27%27...-a017512731|date=1995-10-02|journal=Business Wire|accessdate=2018-09-17|language=en|author=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140504225632/http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Sega+announces+%24299+Sega+Saturn+core+pack%3b+%27%27Virtua+Fighter+Remix%27%27...-a017512731|archivedate=2014-05-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同時，世嘉也將大量SEGA Model-2街機遊戲移植至世嘉土星，至1995年底已有《{{link-en|世嘉冠軍拉力賽車|SEGA Rally Championship}}》、《[[VR戰警|VR戰警]]》及提升幀率至《鐵拳》等級的《[[VR快打2|VR快打2]]》等<ref>cf. {{Cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/jan96/vcop.html|title=Rendered and Ready to Wear|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=1996-01|last=Reiner|first=Andrew|work=Game Informer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19971120011638/http://www.gameinformer.com/jan96/vcop.html|archivedate=1997-11-20|deadurl=yes|language=en}} cf. {{Cite journal|title=Stunning|date=1996-02|journal=Next Generation|issue=14|volume=2|page=162|quote=Totally eliminates the hit or miss polarity of other light-gun games and adds a whole new level of detail to the genre.|language=en}}</ref><ref name="VF2">{{Cite web|url=http://www.next-generation.com/news/113095b.html|title=Virtua Fighter 2 is Here at Last!|accessdate=2018-09-15|work=Next Generation|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19970419221618/http://www.next-generation.com/news/113095b.html|archivedate=1997-04-19|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.allgame.com/game.php?id=1982|title=Virtua Fighter 2|accessdate=2018-09-15|last=Marriott|first=Scott Alan|work=Allgame|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141114131607/http://www.allgame.com/game.php?id=1982|archivedate=2014-11-14|deadurl=yes|language=en}}</ref><ref>cf. {{Cite journal|title=Platinum Pick: Virtua Fighter 2|date=1996-01|journal=Next Generation|issue=13|volume=2|page=179|quote=The ultimate arcade translation ... the best fighting game ever.|language=en}} cf. {{Cite journal|title=Excellent!|date=1996-02|journal=Next Generation|issue=14|volume=2|page=160|quote=A general attention to detail that sets a new mark for quality game design.|language=en}}</ref>，其品質也普遍超越Playstation版本<ref name="RetroinspectionSaturn" /><ref name="US streets">{{Cite journal|title=Sony fights Sega on US streets|language=en|date=1996-01|journal=Next Generation|issue=13|volume=2|pages=14–16}}</ref>。雖然世嘉土星的銷量因此而增加，但已無法挽回Playstation的決定性優勢<ref name="US streets" /><ref name="1995 market share">{{Cite journal|title=Sega captures dollar share of videogame market again; diverse product strategy yields market growth; Sega charts path for 1996.|url=http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Sega+captures+dollar+share+of+videogame+market+--+again%3B+diverse...-a018001580|date=1996-01-10|journal=Business Wire|accessdate=2018-09-17|language=en|author=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502075742/http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Sega%2Bcaptures%2Bdollar%2Bshare%2Bof%2Bvideogame%2Bmarket%2B--%2Bagain%3B%2Bdiverse...-a018001580|archivedate=2014-05-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。至1996年，PlayStation已有世嘉土星數倍的遊戲陣容。1996年6月，世嘉土星新機型於日本發售，售價較初始機型降為199美元<ref name="EGM83">{{Cite journal|title=Saturn Comes Down to Earth|last=|first=|date=1996-06|journal=[[Electronic_Gaming_Monthly|Electronic Gaming Monthly]]|publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]]|issue=83|pages=14–15|language=en}}</ref>。為此，在1996年E3上，索尼也將PlayStation的售價降為199美元<ref name="IGN History of PlayStation" />。儘管雙方皆持續進行[[价格战|價格戰]]，但是由於世嘉土星主機硬體製程複雜，成本不易壓低，使世嘉相對損失更大<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Sony's Video Games Onslaught Continues!|last=|first=|date=1996-06|journal=Maximum: The Video Game Magazine|publisher={{link-en|Emap International Limited}}|issue=7|pages=72–73|language=en}}</ref><ref name="1998 report">{{Cite web|url=http://sega.jp/IR/en/ar/ar1998/ar98.pdf|title=Sega Enterprises Annual Report 1998|accessdate=2018-09-15|publisher=SEGA|pages=1, 7–8|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040504003308/http://sega.jp/IR/en/ar/ar1998/ar98.pdf|archivedate=2004-05-04|deadurl=yes|language=en}}</ref>。

=== 世嘉的鉅變 ===
1990年代中葉，雖然次世代主機如世嘉土星及PlayStation已經上市，但是成本相對較低的16位元家用遊戲機仍有一定市場<ref name=":13" />；1995年，16位元家用遊戲機仍占整體遊戲機市場銷售量的64%<ref name="Innovation and competition2"/><ref name="Lemos2">{{Cite web|url=http://www.zdnet.com/article/sega-makes-play-for-dreamcast-support/|title=Sega makes play for Dreamcast support|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=1999-03-17|last=Lemos|first=Robert|work=[[ZDNet|ZDNet]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217114049/http://www.zdnet.com/article/sega-makes-play-for-dreamcast-support/|archivedate=2014-12-17|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。由於日本世嘉低估了其16位元家用遊戲機[[Mega_Drive|Mega Drive/SEGA Genesis]]的市場潛力，並無近一步投資，因而錯失獲利機會<ref name=":13" /><ref name="1995 market share" /><ref name="Lemos2"/>：僅1995年一年，美國世嘉就售出了2百萬部SEGA Genesis，占了整體遊戲機市場獲利的43%<ref name="1995 market share" />。中山隼雄因Mega Drive在日本的銷量不佳，便決定將研發重心轉移至世嘉土星的決定，是導致世嘉錯失16位元家用遊戲機市場剩餘獲利潛力的主要因素之一<ref name=":13" /><ref name="IGN History of Dreamcast">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2010/09/10/ign-presents-the-history-of-dreamcast|title=IGN Presents the History of Dreamcast|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2010-09-09|last=Fahs|first=Travis|work=IGN|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140928201508/http://www.ign.com/articles/2010/09/10/ign-presents-the-history-of-dreamcast|archivedate=2014-09-28|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。

{{Quote box
|quote=「我相信中山隼雄對電子遊戲的熱情。我們曾討論關於開發電子遊戲硬體的事情，我非常樂意為此協助調整人事及重建世嘉，並全力發展全新的家用遊戲機平臺，因此這次對我來講正是一個不可多得的好機會。」|source=——伯尼·斯托拉爾，於1996年就任美國世嘉總裁時表示。<ref name="IGNHistory_pg6" />|width=30em}}

由於與日本世嘉總部的長期分歧<ref name="IGNHistory_pg6" /><ref name="Tale of Two E3s" />，湯姆·卡林斯基逐漸喪失對世嘉的信心<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.segasammy.co.jp/english/ir/pdf/ir/kako/sega_AR_all_2000.pdf|title=Sega Corporation Annual Report 2000|accessdate=2018-09-15|publisher=SEGA|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070925210504/http://www.segasammy.co.jp/english/ir/pdf/ir/kako/sega_AR_all_2000.pdf|archivedate=2007-09-25|page=18|deadurl=yes|language=en}}</ref>。至1996年初，已有謠傳卡林斯基決定離職<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1999/07/12/business/technology-sega-is-giving-new-product-special-push.html|title=TECHNOLOGY; Sega Is Giving New Product Special Push|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=1999-07-12|last=King|first=Sharon R.|work=The New York Times|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141225075707/http://www.nytimes.com/1999/07/12/business/technology-sega-is-giving-new-product-special-push.html|archivedate=2014-12-25|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>，甚至有日本世嘉總部決定對其美國分公司進行大規模人事調動的消息<ref name="Newsflash2">{{Cite web|url=http://www.next-generation.com/news/071396a.html|title=NEWSFLASH: Sega Planning Drastic Management Reshuffle – World Exclusive|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=1996-07-13|work=Next Generation|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19961220200717/http://www.next-generation.com/news/071396a.html|archivedate=1996-12-20|deadurl=yes|language=en}}</ref>。1996年7月16日，世嘉宣布，前[[本田技研工业|本田]]董事[[入交昭一郎|入交昭一郎]]被任命為美國世嘉總裁兼執行長<ref name="NYT4">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1998/03/14/business/international-business-sega-enterprises-pulls-its-saturn-video-console-us-market.html?pagewanted=1|title=Sega Enterprises Pulls Its Saturn Video Console From the U.S. Market|author=Stephanie Strom|date=1998-03-14|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2018-09-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130430012902/http://www.nytimes.com/1998/03/14/business/international-business-sega-enterprises-pulls-its-saturn-video-console-us-market.html?pagewanted=1|archivedate=2013-04-30|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/library/historical_data/pdf/consolidated_sales_e0912.pdf|title=Consolidated Sales Transition by Region|accessdate=2018-09-15|publisher=Nintendo|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nXieXX2B?url=http://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/library/historical_data/pdf/consolidated_sales_e0912.pdf|archivedate=2010-02-14|deadurl=yes|language=en}}</ref>，而卡林斯基將在當年9月30日之後離開世嘉<ref name="M2 Press" /><ref name="Irimajiri Settles In At Sega"/><ref name="Kalinske out">{{Cite web|url=http://www.next-generation.com/news/071696a.html|title=Kalinske Out – WORLD EXCLUSIVE|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=1996-07-16|work=Next Generation|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19961220200643/http://www.next-generation.com/news/071696a.html|archivedate=1996-12-20|deadurl=yes|language=en}}</ref>。日本世嘉還宣布其聯合創始人{{link-en|大衛·羅森|David Rosen (businessman)}}和現任總裁[[中山隼雄|中山隼雄]]都將辭去現任職位，但兩人仍會留在公司中（中山隼雄並續任日本世嘉執行長）<ref name="M2 Press" /><ref name=":15"/>。同時，前美國[[索尼互動娛樂|索尼電腦娛樂]]執行長{{link-en|伯尼·斯托拉爾|Bernie Stolar}}被任命為美國世嘉負責產品研發和第三方遊戲開發者關係的執行副總裁<ref name="Newsflash2" />。斯托拉爾擁有豐富的交涉經驗，在索尼時曾與開發格鬥遊戲《[[真人快打3|真人快打3]]》的[[Midway|中途遊戲]]訂下3年的獨佔協議{{sfn|Kent|2001|p=506}}，並拉近了與[[艺电|藝電]]的關係<ref name="IGNHistory_pg6" />，世嘉視其為重大人才，賦予重大期望<ref name="Kalinske out" />。

斯托拉爾認為世嘉土星的硬體設計過於複雜，不對世嘉土星抱有期待，還曾在1997年的[[E3电子娱乐展|E3]]上公開表示：「（世嘉）土星不是我們的未來。」<ref name="IGNHistory_pg6" /><ref>{{Cite web|script-title=ja:「セガサターン」はなぜ失敗したのか？当時のCEOが語る|url=https://gigazine.net/news/20170705-sega-saturn-failure/|website=GIGAZINE|date=2018-09-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612140135/https://gigazine.net/news/20170705-sega-saturn-failure/|archivedate=2018-06-12|language=ja|accessdate=2018-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>儘管如此，為了公司的整體戰略，斯托拉爾仍持續試圖為世嘉土星推出高品質遊戲<ref name="IGNHistory_pg6" />，並表示：「為了消費者的利益，即使要（世嘉）土星退場也得慢慢地來。」<ref name="Saturn Overview Manual22">{{Cite journal|title=Saturn Overview Manual|date=1994-06-06|publisher=SEGA|language=en}}</ref>在索尼時，斯托拉爾曾決議將部分日本限定的PlayStation遊戲為美國本土化；在成為世嘉高層後，斯托拉爾也延續此銷售策略<ref name="IGNHistory_pg6" />{{sfn|Kent|2001|p=506}}<ref name="Johnston"/>。同時，世嘉也逐漸轉移至較為溫和的企業定位，將部分過於激進的廣告去除，並更加注重教育相關產業<ref name="Innovation and competition2"/>。

在日本世嘉的戰略規劃下，部分街機部門人員轉為負責開發世嘉土星的獨佔遊戲<ref name="Ages">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/08/08/shenmue-through-the-ages|title=Shenmue: Through the Ages|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2007-08-07|last=Kolan|first=Patrick|work=IGN|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141104113911/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/08/08/shenmue-through-the-ages|archivedate=2014-11-04|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。AM2部門在負責人[[铃木裕|鈴木裕]]的領導下，專為世嘉土星開發獨佔遊戲。其中一款原先具有《VR快打》人物及故事背景的[[電子角色扮演遊戲|角色扮演遊戲]]，經過多次演變增改，成為了一款大型[[開放世界|開放世界]]遊戲，鈴木裕視其為世嘉土星的[[杀手级应用|殺手級遊戲]]<ref name="IGNHistory_pg6" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/news/the-making-of-shenmue-yu-suzuki-on-its-genesis-development-and-the-series-future/|title=The Making of Shenmue: Yu Suzuki on the Cult Classic's Genesis, Development—And Its Future|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2014-03-20|work=Edge|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141215085448/http://www.edge-online.com/news/the-making-of-shenmue-yu-suzuki-on-its-genesis-development-and-the-series-future/|archivedate=2014-12-15|deadurl=yes|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/3/19/5527120/yu-suzuki-shenmue-gdc-2014-classic-game-postmortem|title=Creator Yu Suzuki shares the story of Shenmue's development|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2014-03-19|last=Corriea|first=Alexa Ray|work=Polygon|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150628071042/http://www.polygon.com/2014/3/19/5527120/yu-suzuki-shenmue-gdc-2014-classic-game-postmortem|archivedate=2015-06-28|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。此遊戲最終仍無法趕上世嘉土星的生命週期，後來定名為《[[莎木_一章_橫須賀|莎木]]》，並於世嘉土星的後繼主機[[Dreamcast|Dreamcast]]上發行，成為一代名作<ref name="IGN Shenmue" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The official development system|date=1995-08|journal=Edge|issue=23|volume=3|page=55|language=en}}</ref>。

=== 《音速小子X-Treme》開發中止 ===
{{Main|{{link-en|音速小子X-Treme|Sonic X-Treme}}}}
[[File:Sxtreme-jadegully.jpg|替代=]]
由於[[音速小子|音速小子]]系列的主要開發者[[Sonic_Team|Sonic Team]]正專注於《[[飛天幽夢|飛天幽夢]]》的開發<ref name="Sega-16 STI">{{Cite web|url=http://www.sega-16.com/2007/06/developers-den-sega-technical-institute/|title=Developer's Den: Sega Technical Institute|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2007-06-11|last=Horowitz|first=Ken|work=Sega-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408141746/http://www.sega-16.com/2007/06/developers-den-sega-technical-institute/|archivedate=2016-04-08|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>，因此日本世嘉將開發全新[[三維空間|3D]]音速小子遊戲，即《{{link-en|音速小子X-Treme|Sonic X-Treme}}》（Sonic X-Treme）的任務交給了位於美國的{{link-en|世嘉技術開發研究所|SEGA Technical Institute}}。在開發[[Super_32X|Super 32X]]版本失敗後，開發人員決定將《音速小子X-Treme》的目標發行平台移至世嘉土星<ref name="Sega-16 STI" /><ref name="Fahs revisited">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/05/29/sonic-x-treme-revisited|title=Sonic X-Treme Revisited – Saturn Feature at IGN|accessdate=2018-09-15|author=Fahs, Travis|date=2008-05-29|language=en|work=IGN|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170712125403/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/05/29/sonic-x-treme-revisited|archivedate=2017-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Xtreme">{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/the-greatest-sonic-game-we-never-got-to-play/|title=The greatest Sonic game we never got ...|accessdate=2018-09-15|author=Houghton, David|date=2008-04-24|work=GamesRadar|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Gmmnii8u?url=http://www.gamesradar.com/the-greatest-sonic-game-we-never-got-to-play/|archivedate=2013-05-21|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。《音速小子X-Treme》將以[[魚眼鏡頭|魚眼鏡頭]]的形式顯示關卡，在角色移動的時候關卡也會隨之旋轉。遊戲的開發過程極為艱辛：在日本世嘉高層決定更換[[游戏引擎|遊戲引擎]]後，開發人員被迫重新修改遊戲；為了趕上1996年底的完工期限，開發人員日以繼夜的工作，每日的工作時數甚至達到了16至20小時；雪上加霜的是，原已緩慢的開發進度還因為日本世嘉最終因為授權問題取消了開發人員對遊戲引擎的存取權而付之一炬<ref name="Edge X-Treme">{{Cite journal|title=The Making Of... Sonic X-treme|url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/the-making-of-sonic-x-treme/|last=|first=|date=2007-07|journal=[[Edge_(magazine)|Edge]]|publisher=[[Future_plc|Future plc]]|issue=177|volume=15|pages=100–103|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130417052400/http://www.edge-online.com/features/the-making-of-sonic-x-treme/|archivedate=2013-04-17|deadurl=yes|via=Edge Online|language=en|access-date=2018-08-12}}</ref><ref name="Fahs revisited" /><ref name="Xtreme" />。最後在主要開發人員奧弗·阿龍（Ofer Alon）離職、{{link-en|克里斯·辛 (電子遊戲設計師)|Chris Senn (video game designer)|克里斯·辛}}及克里斯·柯芬（Chris Coffin）等人接連病倒後，《音速小子X-Treme》於1997年初中止開發<ref name="Edge X-Treme" /><ref name="Fahs revisited" /><ref name="Xtreme" />。之後Sonic Team雖一度計畫為世嘉土星開發3D音速小子遊戲，不過由於世嘉土星銷售的頹勢而將研發重點轉往下一代主機[[Dreamcast|Dreamcast]]<ref>{{Cite web |last=Barnholt |first=Ray |url=http://www.1up.com/features/yuji-naka-interview-ivy-kiwi?pager.offset=2 |title=Yuji Naka Interview: Ivy the Kiwi and a Little Sega Time Traveling |work=1UP.com |accessdate=2016-12-10 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140304180628/http://www.1up.com/features/yuji-naka-interview-ivy-kiwi?pager.offset=2 |archivedate=2014-03-04 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Relief">{{Cite web|last=Towell|first=Justin|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/super-rare-1990-sonic-the-hedgehog-prototype-is-missing/|title=Super-rare 1990 Sonic The Hedgehog prototype is missing|work=GamesRadar|date=2012-06-23|accessdate=2014-03-04|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160324080928/http://www.gamesradar.com/super-rare-1990-sonic-the-hedgehog-prototype-is-missing/|archivedate=2016-03-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

輿論多對《音速小子X-Treme》開發中止表示遺憾。[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]的大衛·霍頓（David Houghton）認為世嘉土星擁有優質3D音速小子遊戲與否的重要性「在某種方面上與恐龍滅絕與否相當」<ref name="Xtreme"/>；[[IGN|IGN]]的塔維斯·法斯（Tavis Fahs）稱《音速小子X-Treme》為「音速小子系列、世嘉的32位元電子遊戲機，以及世嘉本身情勢的轉捩點」<ref name="Fahs revisited"/>；在世嘉土星生命週期期間經營粉絲向網站的戴夫·西卓科（Dave Zdyrko）則表示：「我不知道《音速小子X-Treme》能不能真的拯救世嘉土星的頹勢，但是明明音速小子系列在Genesis時代一直是主機銷量的關鍵要素，為什麼世嘉沒有在世嘉土星發售前就準備好一款幾乎保證可以大幅提升買氣的音速小子遊戲呢？」<ref name="1UP Pleasure and Pain"/>在2007年的一次訪談中，《音速小子X-Treme》的製作人麥克·沃利斯（Mike Wallis）表示遊戲「絕對有與《[[超級瑪利歐64|超級瑪利歐64]]》一拼的實力」<ref name="Edge X-Treme"/> ；不過《{{link-en|Next Generation (magazine)|Next Generation (雜誌)|Next Generation}}》於1996年底的報導中稱《音速小子X-Treme》品質可能無法與當時市面上的其他遊戲媲美，並表示如果遊戲貿然發售將損害世嘉的商譽<ref>{{Cite magazine|last=|first= |title=In the Studio|magazine=Next Generation|issue=23 |publisher=[[Imagine_Media|Imagine Media]] |date=November 1996|page=17|language=en}}</ref>；中裕司並表示在聽聞《音速小子X-Treme》開發中止後覺得放心，因為「遊戲品質以我的角度來看並不如預期」<ref name="Relief"/>。

=== 停產 ===
雖然自1993年起，世嘉的獲利開始隨著整體電子遊戲產業的趨勢下滑，但是仍相對維持在領導地位<ref name="Finn" />。1996年初時，世嘉仍占有北美家用遊戲機市場的38%，領先對手任天堂的30%及索尼的24%<ref name="Innovation and competition2"/>。但是，[[PlayStation_(遊戲機)|PlayStation]]和世嘉土星的差距愈加明顯：1995年底時，索尼在北美市場已售出80萬部[[PlayStation_(遊戲機)|PlayStation]]，是世嘉同時間售出之世嘉土星數量的2倍之多<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/a_playstationhistory_1|title=PlayStation-The total history|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2006-11-20|last=McCarthy|first=Dave|work=Eurogamer|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129070933/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/a_playstationhistory_1|archivedate=2014-11-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>；同時，Mega Drive/SEGA Genesis的銷量也開始銳減<ref name=":13" /><ref name="Innovation and competition2"/>。至1996年底，索尼總計在北美市場已售出290萬部PlayStation，大幅超越世嘉售出的120萬部世嘉土星<ref name="Schilling" />。儘管雙方皆持續進行[[价格战|價格戰]]<ref name="Finn" />，但是由於世嘉土星主機硬體製程複雜，成本不易壓低，使世嘉赤字日益嚴重<ref name=":13" /><ref>西田宗千佳. 《<bdi lang="ja">美学vs.実利 「チーム久夛良木」対任天堂の総力戦15年史</bdi>》. 講談社. 2008: 114-115 {{ja icon}}</ref>。

1996年6月，任天堂的次世代主機[[任天堂64|任天堂64]]發布，其飛躍性的3D運算效能，使世嘉土星原本已搖搖欲墜的銷量急轉直下<ref name=":15">{{Cite journal|title=Battle of the Games|last=Day|first=Rebecca|date=1996-12|journal={{link-en|Popular Mechanics}}|issue=12|volume=173|page=52|language=en}}</ref>。1997年初，[[史克威爾|史克威爾]]在PlayStation平台上發行《[[最终幻想VII|最終幻想VII]]》，獲得極大成功，更對世嘉土星造成毀滅性的打擊<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/making-final-fantasy-vii/3/|title=The Making Of: Final Fantasy VII|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2012-08-26|work=Edge|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141026033706/http://www.edge-online.com/features/making-final-fantasy-vii/3/|archivedate=2014-10-26|page=3|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。1997年，索尼在北美市場售出的PlayStation主機數量已達世嘉售出之世嘉土星數量的3倍之多<ref name="Finn" />。此時，索尼已占有北美家用遊戲機市場額的47%，超越了任天堂的40%及世嘉的僅僅12%，無論是降低售價還是推出任何新遊戲都已經不能扭轉世嘉土星的劣勢<ref name="NYT4" /><ref name=":24">{{Cite web|url=http://www.telecompaper.com/news/sega-sales-fall-in-1sthalf--123315|title=Sega Sales Fall in First Half|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=1997-11-21|work=Telecompaper|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151105061708/http://www.telecompaper.com/news/sega-sales-fall-in-1sthalf--123315|archivedate=2015-11-05|deadurl=yes|language=en}}</ref><ref name=":15"/>。由於世嘉土星在北美地區的表現不佳，美國世嘉在1997年下半年資遣了60名員工<ref name="NYT4" />。

{{Quote box
|quote=「我認為（世嘉）土星最大的敗筆在於其硬體架構。遊戲開發者再怎麼優秀，在複雜的硬體限制之下都無法發揮全力。遊戲顯然是了不起的，但硬體並沒有達到那個水準。」|source=——伯尼·斯托拉爾，於2009年一次採訪中表示。<ref name="IGNHistory_pg6" />|width=30em}}

由於公司財務狀況惡化，中山隼雄於1998年1月辭去日本世嘉總裁<ref name="NYT4" />。1998年3月，由於獲利不斷下降，日本世嘉自1988年在[[東京證券交易所|東京證券交易所]]上市以來，第一次遭受合併財務損失，公司合併淨虧損達356億日圓<ref name="1998 report" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/sega-news-from-japan/1100-2462352/|title=Sega News From Japan|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=1998-03-18|work=GameSpot|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170705034437/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/sega-news-from-japan/1100-2462352/|archivedate=2017-07-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同時，美國世嘉宣布世嘉土星將退出北美家用遊戲機市場，以專注於其繼任者，即[[Dreamcast|Dreamcast]]的研發<ref name="NYT4" /><ref name=":15"/>。1998年，在北美僅有12款世嘉土星遊戲推出（包括最後一款官方發行的遊戲《[[魔法騎士雷阿斯|魔法騎士雷阿斯]]》），相較於1996年的116款大幅縮減<ref name="Lemos2"/><ref name="IGN History of Dreamcast" /><ref name=":17" />。日本及歐洲地區的支援及服務則延續至2000年<ref name="brandweek">{{Cite journal|title=Looking for a Sonic Boom|language=en|author=Lefton, Terry|journal=Brandweek|issue=39|year=1998|volume=9|pages=26–29}}</ref>。1998年11月，世嘉土星的後繼主機[[Dreamcast|Dreamcast]]於日本首發<ref name=":13" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Saturn Gets Hooked Up|last=|first=|date=1996-05|journal=[[Electronic_Gaming_Monthly|Electronic Gaming Monthly]]|publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]]|issue=82|page=20|language=en}}</ref>。2007年，日本世嘉完全中止世嘉土星的維修服務<ref>{{Cite web|title=|url=http://sega.jp/topics/070330_1/home.shtml|accessdate=2019-07-01|date=2007-10-01|publisher=SEGA|language=ja|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130706134051/http://sega.jp/topics/070330_1/home.shtml|archivedate=2013-07-06|script-title=ja:『セガサターン』『Dreamcast』有償修理終了のお知らせ|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

世嘉土星在日本銷量約575萬部、北美銷量約180萬部、歐洲銷量約100萬部、其他地區銷量約53萬部，總計約926萬部<ref name="CESA" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Goodbye (?!) Sega Saturn|date=2000-04-07|journal=Dreamcast Magazine|issue=12|volume=3|page=154|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|title=The Video Game Industry: Formation, Present State, and Future|first1=Peter|last2=Wilson|first2=Timothy L.|last3=Ernkvist|first3=Mirko|publisher=Routledge|year=2012|isbn=978-1138803831|page=158|chapter=Console Hardware: The Development of Nintendo Wii|last1=Zackariasson|language=en}}</ref><ref name="Sega Stats">{{Cite journal|title=Weekly Famitsu Express|date=1996-06-21|issue=392|volume=11|page=8|work=Famitsu|language=en}}</ref>，自商業角度來看是失敗的<ref name="brandweek" />。世嘉土星的失敗有著諸多緣由，其中最重要的是世嘉自身商業布局的失誤：在[[北美地区|北美地區]]的發售由於操之過急，發售時間比原先預定早了四個月，導致[[游戏开发者|第三方遊戲開發商]]沒有時間製作遊戲、零售商沒有時間宣傳，世嘉與零售商之間的關係因此惡化<ref name="Schilling" />；再加上任天堂開發次世代主機的時程過於緩慢，最終造成索尼的[[PlayStation_(遊戲機)|PlayStation]]成功獲得領先地位<ref name=":13" /><ref name="Finn" />{{sfn|DeMaria|Wilson|2004|pages=282–283}}。

== 硬體 ==
=== 技術規格 ===
[[File:SEGA_Saturn_System_Hardware_Process.png|替代=]]
<gallery>
File:HD6417095 01.jpg|[[日立製作所|日立]] SH-2<br>[[中央處理器|中央處理器]]（客製版）
File:315-5687 01.jpg|[[山葉公司|山葉]] YMF292<br>音效處理器（客製版）
File:Ss chip 315-5688 01.jpg|[[世嘉|世嘉]] FH3007<br>系統控制器
File:315-5689 01.jpg|世嘉 VDP1<br>[[圖形處理器|圖形處理器]]
File:315-5690 VDP2 01.jpg|世嘉 VDP2<br>[[圖形處理器|圖形處理器]]
</gallery>
世嘉土星主機之長、寬、高分別為260[[毫米|公釐]]×230公釐×83公釐（10.2[[英寸|英寸]]×9.1英寸×3.3英寸）<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":14"/><ref name=":222">{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/Sega_Saturn_hardware_notes_(2004-04-27)|title=Sega Saturn hardware notes - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-13|work=SEGA Retro|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814134830/https://segaretro.org/Sega_Saturn_hardware_notes_(2004-04-27)|archivedate=2018-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

世嘉土星採用雙[[中央處理器|中央處理器]]（CPU）設計<ref name=":222" /><ref name="Allgame2">{{Cite web|url=http://www.allgame.com/platform.php?id=26&tab=overview|title=Sega Saturn – Overview|accessdate=2018-09-15|author=Beuscher, Dave|work=[[Allgame|Allgame]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141114110452/http://www.allgame.com/platform.php?id=26&tab=overview|archivedate=2014-11-14|deadurl=yes|language=en}}</ref>，主機內含有兩顆由[[日立製作所|日立]]製造的[[SuperH|SH-2]][[精簡指令集|精簡指令集]]（RISC）[[32位元|32位元]][[微處理器|微處理器]]，快取為4[[千字节|KB]]，[[每秒指令|每秒指令數]]（IPS）可達2500萬次，同時世嘉還特別將處理器頻率由20MHz[[超頻|超頻]]為28.6MHz，以符合主機實際運算需求<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":14" /><ref name="NG February" /><ref name="NextGenDec" /><ref name=":222" />。

{{Quote box|quote=「多數的開發人員並沒有辦法同時活用兩顆中央處理器——大部分的遊戲最多只能使用1.5顆處理器的效能。我認為，在所有世嘉土星遊戲的開發人員中，只有大概百分之一的人能真正發揮（世嘉）土星的硬體潛能。」|source=——鈴木裕，於回顧《[[VR快打2|VR快打2]]》的開發時表示。<ref name="NG February"/>|width=30em}}

SH-2處理器採用了當時最先進的[[乘法器|乘法器]]（multiplier）技術，使世嘉土星能實現更精確快速的幾何圖形演算。不過由於世嘉土星的兩顆SH-2處理器是使用同一[[总线|匯流排]]存取記憶體，因此在協同運算的時候容易造成混亂；雖然世嘉土星具備一定的[[多元處理|多元處理]]機能，能透過匯流排仲裁（Bus Arbitration）機能協調部分處理器運算，但是因為其複雜的硬體架構，使得開發遊戲仍十分困難，加上世嘉土星遊戲開發使用的程式語言為較困難的[[組合語言|組合語言]]，世嘉也沒有提供完整的[[函式庫|函數庫]]，造成大部分遊戲仍只使用單顆處理器進行運算，另一顆處理器則多只用於處理雜務<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":13" /><ref name=":14" /><ref name=":222" />{{sfn|Kent|2001|p=509. "In theory, Saturn, which featured two Hitachi SH2 32-bit central processing chips, was more powerful than PlayStation. The truth was that the SH2 chips were somewhat inferior to the chip Sony had selected ... and allotting different operations to both of the processing chips proved nearly impossible"}}。另外，世嘉還在世嘉土星的光碟機中加入了一顆日立的[[SuperH|SH-1]]微處理器作為輔助，以加快讀取速度<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":14" /><ref name="Edge Japanese launch" /><ref name=":222" />。由於世嘉土星內部處理器繁多、運算架構複雜，因此世嘉引入自製的FH3007系統控制器（SCU），透過其[[數位訊號處理|數位訊號處理]]及[[直接記憶體存取|直接記憶體存取]]等機能管理及協調眾多處理器元件<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":13" /><ref name=":14" /><ref name=":222" />。

世嘉土星預設以[[AV端子|AV端子]]輸出訊號，[[帧率|幀率]]最高可達每秒60[[幀|幀]]<ref name="VF2" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/index.php?title=File:ST-013-R3-061694.pdf&page=6|title=ST-013-R3-061694.pdf - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-13|work=SEGA Retro|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814134826/https://segaretro.org/index.php?title=File:ST-013-R3-061694.pdf&page=6|archivedate=2018-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[解析度|解析度]]為320×224<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":13" /><ref name=":222" />（最高可達704×480<ref name="ST-103" /><ref name=":222" /><ref name=":202">{{Cite journal|title=VDP1 User Manual|date=1995-06-27|publisher=Sega of America|page=134|language=en}}</ref>）。世嘉土星以24位元[[真彩色|真彩]]發色，同時發色數最高為1677萬色<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":13" />。世嘉土星擁有兩顆[[圖形處理器|圖形處理器]]（GPU）（官方稱之為視訊顯示處理器（Video Display Processor，VDP）<ref name=":16" /><ref name="RetroinspectionSaturn" /><ref name=":13" /><ref name=":14" />），分別為主要負責繪製[[精灵图|精靈圖]]（sprite）、[[材质贴图|貼圖]]（texture）及[[多邊形|多邊形]]的VDP1（Video Display Processor 1）及主要負責繪製背景圖層（background）的VDP2（Video Display Processor 2）<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":14" /><ref name="Saturn Overview Manual22" /><ref name=":202" /><ref name=":212">{{Cite web|url=http://www.shinforce.com/saturn/information/3D-Capabilities.htm|title=Sega Saturn 3D Capabilities|accessdate=2018-08-13|last=Musashi|first=Joe Shinobi|work=Shin Force|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171021031344/http://www.shinforce.com/saturn/information/3D-Capabilities.htm|archivedate=2017-10-21|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。另外，世嘉土星擁有三顆也具有幾何運算能力的[[數位訊號處理器|數位訊號處理器]]（DSP），兩顆嵌入於中央處理器中，一顆則嵌入於系統控制器中<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":14" /><ref name="Saturn Overview Manual22" />。

VDP1主要負責主要負責繪製[[精灵图|精靈圖]]、[[材质贴图|貼圖]]及[[多邊形|多邊形]]等高動態物件<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":272">{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/VDP1_(Saturn)|title=VDP1 - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-13|author=|date=|work=SEGA Retro|publisher=|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171004214319/http://segaretro.org/VDP1_(Saturn)|archivedate=2017-10-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。身為次世代主機，世嘉土星擁有大幅超越16位元遊戲機的[[二维计算机图形|2D圖形]]運算能力，除了一般的擴大縮小、扭曲、變形、半透明、陰影等特殊顯示效果之外<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":222" /><ref name=":202" /><ref name=":272" />，還具備將2D精靈圖賦予3D座標變形處理，藉以繪製以[[四邊形|四邊形]]為基礎單位之多邊形的機能，每秒最多可繪製500,000個多邊形、渲染100,000個多邊形<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":13" /><ref name=":222" /><ref name=":202" /><ref name=":212" /><ref name=":272" /><ref name="DreisbachCG2">{{Cite web|url=http://curmudgeongamer.com/article.php?story=20021008212903265|title=Interview: Ezra Dreisbach|accessdate=2018-09-15|date=2002-07-09|work=Curmudgeon Gamer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927211250/http://curmudgeongamer.com/article.php?story=20021008212903265|language=en|archivedate=2007-09-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

世嘉土星並不是一部以3D繪圖為出發點的主機<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":212" /><ref name=":272" />：世嘉土星原先只有一顆圖形處理器VDP1，但在開發過程中，為加強[[三维计算机图形|3D圖形]]運算能力，藉此與[[索尼|索尼]]即將推出的全新家用遊戲機[[PlayStation|PlayStation]]抗衡，而加入另一[[圖形處理器|圖形處理器]]VDP2，使VDP1得以專注處理[[三维计算机图形|3D圖形]]運算<ref name=":13" /><ref name="NG February" /><ref name="NextGenDec" /><ref name="NG January" /><ref name=":182" /><ref name=":282">{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/VDP2_(Saturn)|title=VDP2 - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-14|author=|date=|work=SEGA Retro|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003231122/http://segaretro.org/VDP2_(Saturn)|archivedate=2017-10-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。VDP2主要負責繪製背景圖層，不過有時候也會分擔部分的前景運算工作<ref name="NextGenDec" /><ref name="VF2" /><ref name=":222" /><ref name=":282" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.next-generation.com/saturn/specs.html|title=Saturn Technical Specs|accessdate=2018-09-15|work=Next Generation|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19961220175019/http://www.next-generation.com/saturn/specs.html|archivedate=1996-12-20|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。VDP2可同時顯示最多5層圖層，並支援擴大縮小、扭曲、變形、半透明、陰影等特殊顯示效果<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":222" /><ref name=":212" /><ref name=":282" />，還可以將VDP1繪製的畫面作為單一圖層合成至[[帧缓冲器|訊框緩衝器]]（frame buffer）進一步調整，其強大的性能使世嘉土星能近乎完美的移植街機遊戲<ref name="VF2" /><ref name=":222" /><ref name=":212" /><ref name=":282" />。

世嘉土星以[[摩托羅拉|摩托羅拉]]的客製版[[摩托罗拉_68000|摩托羅拉68000]]微處理器為音效控制器（SCU），頻率為11.3MHz<ref name=":16" />；音效處理器（SPU）本身則採用[[山葉公司|山葉]]的客製版YMF292處理器，並搭載專用的音訊數位訊號處理器FH1，頻率為22.6[[MHz|MHz]]<ref name=":15"/>，可使用[[頻率調變|頻率調變]]（FM，8個頻道）及[[脈衝編碼調變|脈波編碼調變]]（PCM，24個頻道），共計32個音訊[[頻道|頻道]]生成聲音，取樣率最高可達44.1[[Hz|KHz]]<ref name=":16" /><ref name="Saturn Overview Manual22"/>。

[[File:Sega-Saturn-4MB.jpg|替代=]]]]
世嘉土星擁有約2[[百萬位元組|MB]]（16Mbit）的主記憶體、約1.5MB（12Mbit）的[[VRAM|視訊隨機存取記憶體]]（VRAM）、約32KB（256Kbit）的緊急備份用記憶體及CD-ROM與音效用記憶體各約512KB（4Mbit），共計約4.5MB（36Mbit）<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":222" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/index.php?title=File:Sega_Service_Manual_-_Sega_Saturn_(PAL)_-_013-1_-_June_1995.pdf&page=12|title=Sega Service Manual - Sega Saturn (PAL) - 013-1 - June 1995.pdf - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-13|work=SEGA Retro|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814134949/https://segaretro.org/index.php?title=File:Sega_Service_Manual_-_Sega_Saturn_(PAL)_-_013-1_-_June_1995.pdf&page=12|archivedate=2018-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/index.php?title=File:13-APR-94.pdf&page=8|title=13-APR-94.pdf - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-13|work=SEGA Retro|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806233022/http://segaretro.org/index.php?title=File:13-APR-94.pdf&page=8|archivedate=2017-08-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>，各自獨立運作，並透過系統控制器協調分配<ref name=":222" />。主記憶體前半由[[同步動態隨機存取記憶體|同步動態隨機存取記憶體]]（SDRAM）構成，主要負責遊戲本體數據及視訊畫面輸出等需要較快速度的工作；後半則由速度較慢的[[動態隨機存取記憶體|動態隨機存取記憶體]]（DRAM）構成，此部分可透過將外接配件「擴充記憶體卡」（{{lang|ja|拡張ラムカートリッジ}}，分為1MB版及4MB版，HSS-0150/HSS-0167）插入主機的卡帶插槽擴充。由於用以控制記憶體的SH-2處理器本身的機能限制，最多可擴充4.5MB（36Mbit），使主機記憶體最大可用容量增加至9MB（72Mbit）<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":13" /><ref name=":222" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/File:HM514260C_datasheet.pdf|title=HM514260C datasheet.pdf - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-13|work=SEGA Retro|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806185329/http://segaretro.org/File:HM514260C_datasheet.pdf|archivedate=2017-08-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，世嘉土星主機上方有一個[[同步動態隨機存取記憶體|同步動態隨機存取記憶體]]（SDRAM）插槽，用以擴充[[電腦記憶體|記憶體]]，提升主機運算速度。由於用以控制記憶體存取的SH-2處理器本身的機能限制，世嘉土星之記憶體最多只能擴充4MB（32Mbit）<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":14" /><ref name=":222" /><ref>{{Cite web|script-title=ja:セガのハードに込められた熱意が語られた GAME ONトークイベント“セガハードの歴史を語り尽くす”詳細リポート|url=http://www.famitsu.com/news/201606/03107324.html?page=2|website=[[Fami通|Fami通]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613134033/http://www.famitsu.com/news/201606/03107324.html?page=2|archivedate=2018-06-13|language=ja|date=2016-06-03|accessdate=2018-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":182">{{Cite web|script-title=ja:中 裕司がアツく語った『ソニック』『大魔界村』そしてメガドラ愛。幻のメガドラタイトルのお披露目も！？【ゲームセンターCX放送作家の「いまさらメガドラ計画」】第2回|url=http://news.denfaminicogamer.jp/megadrivecx/kibe2|website=電ファミニコゲーマー|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612143449/http://news.denfaminicogamer.jp/megadrivecx/kibe2|archivedate=2018-06-12|language=ja|date=2016-07-07|deadurl=no|accessdate=2018-08-14}}</ref>。原先世嘉打算同時發行採用[[CD-ROM|CD-ROM]]及採用[[ROM卡带|ROM卡帶]]兩種版本的主機，不過由於卡帶遊戲成本過高、儲存空間不足而放棄了卡帶版本<ref name="NG February" />。

世嘉土星使用雙倍速的[[CD-ROM|CD-ROM]][[光碟機|光碟機]]，並以日立的[[SuperH|SH-1]]微處理器輔助，以加快讀取速度<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":14" /><ref name="Edge Japanese launch" /><ref name=":222" />；光碟本身之容量為540MB<ref name=":252" />。另外，為了防止盜版，在遊戲光碟的最外層加入了特殊讀寫層「世嘉土星環」為防[[盜版|盜版]]機制<ref name=":13" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://gigazine.net/news/20160712-sega-saturn-crack/|script-title=ja:20年以上の時を超えてセガサターンをクラックした猛者が登場|newspaper=GIGAZINE|accessdate=2018-08-13|language=ja|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814170019/https://gigazine.net/news/20160712-sega-saturn-crack/|archivedate=2018-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於為CD-ROM配置了專用記憶體，世嘉土星在運行同一款遊戲時，通常較競爭對手[[PlayStation|PlayStation]]流暢，畫面中斷或延遲的情形也幾乎不會出現<ref name="#1"/><ref name=":222" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/File:HM514260_datasheet.pdf|title=HM514260 datasheet.pdf - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-13|work=SEGA Retro|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814134840/https://segaretro.org/File:HM514260_datasheet.pdf|archivedate=2018-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://github.com/mamedev/mame/blob/master/src/mame/drivers/saturn.cpp|title=mamedev/mame|accessdate=2018-08-13|work=GitHub|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116032259/https://github.com/mamedev/mame/blob/master/src/mame/drivers/saturn.cpp|archivedate=2018-11-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 機型 ===
<gallery widths="175" heights="120">
File:Sega-Saturn-JP-Mk1-Console-Set.png|日版世嘉土星初始機型<br>（HST-3200/HST-3210）
File:Sega-Saturn-JP-Mk2-Console-Set.png|日版世嘉土星後期機型<br>（HST-3220）
File:Sega-Saturn-Console-Set-Mk1.png|美版世嘉土星初始機型<br>（MK-80000）
File:Sega-Saturn-Console-Set-Mk2.png|美版世嘉土星後期機型<br>（MK-80000A）
</gallery>
世嘉土星在其生命週期中，曾進行多次改版，世嘉也多次授權第三方廠商發行客製化版本。此外，北美版本的世嘉土星也與日本原版有著些許差異。

初版世嘉土星（HST-3200）於1994年11月22日發售，售價為44800[[日圓|日圓]]；外殼為灰色，其主要辨識特徵為主機前部的左側有一個圓形的[[通氣|通氣口]]<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":13" />。1995年，世嘉將世嘉土星的結構進行細微調整後重新推出（HST-3210），售價也降至34800日圓。與初代機型最大的不同是通氣口減少、電源和讀取指示燈只剩一個LED燈等<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":14" />。在與[[PlayStation_(遊戲機)|PlayStation]]的競爭愈趨下風之後，世嘉土星再度改版，將兩個中央處理器合併於同一芯片上以節省成本，外殼也改為較廉價的白色，並於1996年3月，以初代機型售價近二分之一的20000日圓發售（HST-3220）<ref name=":13" /><ref name="EGM83" /><ref name=":252">{{Cite web|url=https://sega.jp/history/hard/segasaturn/devices.html|script-title=ja:セガハード大百科 - セガサターン - 関連・周辺機器|accessdate=2018-08-14|work=セガハード大百科|publisher=SEGA|language=ja|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711231301/https://sega.jp/history/hard/segasaturn/devices.html|archivedate=2018-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":262">{{Cite web|url=https://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/saturn.html|title=[セガハード大百科] セガサターン - 関連・周辺機器|accessdate=2018-08-14|work=SEGA|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814135306/https://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/saturn.html|archivedate=2018-08-14|dead-url=no|language=ja}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Sega Reveals a New Saturn!!!|last=Hunter|first=Yasuhiro|date=1996-05|journal=Maximum: The Video Game Magazine|publisher={{link-en|Emap International Limited}}|issue=6|page=127|language=en}}</ref>。由於對硬體規格進行了大幅縮減，新版世嘉土星失去了對部分硬體要求較高遊戲的[[相容性|相容性]]<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":222" /><ref name=":252" /><ref name=":262" />。同時，世嘉也授權部分第三方廠商發行客製化版本，包括[[JVC|勝利]]推出的「V土星」（{{lang|ja|Ｖサターン}}，RG-JX1/RG-JX2），[[日立製作所|日立]]推出的「Hi土星」（{{lang|ja|ハイサターン}}，MMP-1/MMP-1-1/MMP-1-2/MMP-11）與專為車用[[導航系統|導航系統]]製造的「遊戲&導航 Hi土星」（{{lang|ja|ゲーム＆カーナビ ハイサターン}}，MMP-1000NV），以及[[三星電子|三星]]推出的「三星土星」（{{lang|ko|삼성새턴}}，SPC-SATURN/SPC-SATURN II）等<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":13" /><ref name=":14" /><ref name=":10" /><ref name=":252" /><ref name="HISATURN2">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hitachi.co.jp/New/cnews/9512/1201.html|script-title=ja:ポータブルマルチメディアプレーヤー 「ゲーム＆カーナビ ハイサターン」を発売|accessdate=2018-09-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180331203238/http://www.hitachi.co.jp/New/cnews/9512/1201.html|archivedate=2018-03-31|dead-url=no|language=ja}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=On the Move!|date=1996-02|work={{link-en|Sega Saturn Magazine}}|issue=4|volume=2|page=9|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Saturn consoles in South Korea - Sega Retro|url=https://segaretro.org/Saturn_consoles_in_South_Korea|work=SEGA Retro|accessdate=2019-04-29|author=|date=|publisher=|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331044841/https://segaretro.org/Saturn_consoles_in_South_Korea|archivedate=2019-03-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

初代北美版本的世嘉土星（MK-80000，與日版HST-3200/HST-3210機型硬體架構相同）於1995年5月11日發售，售價為399美元<ref name="This Day" />（隨後降價至299美元<ref name=":9" />）；整體外型延續了前代家用遊戲機[[Mega_Drive|SEGA Genesis]]的設計風格，外殼為純黑色，[[識別標誌|識別標誌]]也與日版有所差異，並搭配了專為北美玩家設計的控制器<ref name="RetroinspectionSaturn" /><ref name=":13" /><ref name="1UP Pleasure and Pain" /><ref name="This Day" />。在日版世嘉土星改版後，美版隨後跟進，於1995年6月發售更新版本（MK-80000A，與日版HST-3220機型硬體架構相同），售價也降為199美元<ref name="EGM83" />；雖然內部結構大致和日版世嘉土星相同，不過整體外型改動較日版少；搭配的控制器則改為與日版相同形狀，但外觀顏色仍為黑色<ref name="EGM83" /><ref name=":29">{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/Control_Pad_(Saturn)|title=Control Pad - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-14|author=|date=|work=SEGA Retro|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814134856/https://segaretro.org/Control_Pad_(Saturn)|archivedate=2018-08-14|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref><ref name=":30">{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/Press_release:_1996-09-17:_Sega_brings_fun_and_games,_ease-of-use_to_TV_Internet_market|title=Press release: 1996-09-17: Sega brings fun and games, ease-of-use to TV Internet market - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-14|work=SEGA Retro|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170918180948/http://segaretro.org/Press_release:_1996-09-17:_Sega_brings_fun_and_games,_ease-of-use_to_TV_Internet_market|archivedate=2017-09-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 配件 ===
<gallery widths="150" heights="120">
File:Sega-Saturn-JP-Mk1-Controller.jpg|日版世嘉土星控制器<br>（HSS-0101）
File:Sega-Saturn-Controller-Mk-I-NA-FL.jpg|美版世嘉土星控制器<br>（MK-80100）
File:Sega-Saturn-JP-3D-Pad.jpg|日版世嘉土星3D控制器<br>（HSS-0103）
File:Volant Sega Saturn.jpg|美版世嘉土星方向盤控制器<br>（MK-80107）
File:Sega-Saturn-Multitap.jpg|美版世嘉土星控制器擴充座<br>（MK-80102）
File:Sega-Saturn-NetLink.jpg|美版SEGA Net Link數據機<br>（MK-80118）
</gallery>
世嘉土星隨附的控制器之整體設計延續自前代家用遊戲機[[Mega_Drive|Mega Drive/SEGA Genesis]]的6鍵控制器，並改善十字鍵構造及控制器握感，被譽為「最適合用以遊玩2D格鬥遊戲的控制器」，在世嘉土星停產後還曾多次推出復刻版<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":252" /><ref name=":29" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/pad.html|script-title=ja:[セガハード大百科] セガサターンコントロールパッド|accessdate=2018-08-15|work=SEGA|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710143119/http://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/pad.html|archivedate=2016-07-10|dead-url=no|language=ja}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://venturebeat.com/2010/04/14/the-sega-saturn-controller-greatest-or-merely-bestest/|title=The Sega Saturn Controller: Greatest, Or Merely Bestest?|date=2010-04-14|newspaper=VentureBeat|accessdate=2018-08-15|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180817130534/https://venturebeat.com/2010/04/14/the-sega-saturn-controller-greatest-or-merely-bestest/|archivedate=2018-08-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>；此外，因應玩家需求，也研發了以紅外線與主機連線的無線版本<ref name=":13" /><ref name=":252" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/codeless.html|script-title=ja:[セガハード大百科] セガサターンコードレスパッド|accessdate=2018-08-15|work=SEGA|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160514031114/http://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/codeless.html|archivedate=2016-05-14|dead-url=no|language=ja}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/Saturn_Infrared_Control_Pad|title=Saturn Infrared Control Pad - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-15|work=SEGA Retro|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171124020551/http://segaretro.org/Saturn_Infrared_Control_Pad|archivedate=2017-11-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。初代美版世嘉土星於1995年推出時，曾特別搭配了針對北美玩家的控制器，形狀與日版控制器有些許不同<ref name="RetroinspectionSaturn" /><ref name=":13" /><ref name="1UP Pleasure and Pain" /><ref name=":29" />；不過在世嘉土星改版後，搭配的控制器也改為與日版相同形狀<ref name="EGM83" /><ref name=":29" /><ref name=":30" />。後來為抗衡[[任天堂|任天堂]]推出的[[任天堂64|任天堂64]]，在《[[飛天幽夢|飛天幽夢]]》發售後，世嘉也隨之推出附有[[類比搖桿|類比搖桿]]的3D控制器<ref name=":13" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/3D_Control_Pad|title=3D Control Pad - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-15|work=SEGA Retro|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180410095700/https://segaretro.org/3D_Control_Pad|archivedate=2018-04-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.satakore.com/sega-saturn-store-game,,81048,,Nights-Into-Dreams...-with-3D-Control-Pad-USA.html|title=Buy Nights Into Dreams with 3D Control Pad|accessdate=2018-08-15|work=satakore|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160807014523/http://www.satakore.com/sega-saturn-store-game,,81048,,Nights-Into-Dreams...-with-3D-Control-Pad-USA.html|archivedate=2016-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>；另外，還曾為不同種類的街機遊戲推出「街機專業控制器」（{{lang|ja|バーチャスティック}}，HSS-0104/HSS-0136）<ref name=":252" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/stick.html|script-title=ja:[セガハード大百科] バーチャスティック|accessdate=2018-08-15|work=SEGA|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710143124/http://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/stick.html|archivedate=2016-07-10|dead-url=no|language=ja}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/Virtua_Stick|title=Virtua Stick - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-15|work=SEGA Retro|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180604223313/https://segaretro.org/Virtua_Stick|archivedate=2018-06-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>、「模擬飛行用控制器」（{{lang|ja|ミッションスティック}}，HSS-0114）<ref name=":252" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/mission.html|script-title=ja:[セガハード大百科] アナログミッションスティック|accessdate=2018-08-15|work=SEGA|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710143258/http://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/mission.html|archivedate=2016-07-10|dead-url=no|language=ja}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/Mission_Stick|title=Mission Stick - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-15|work=SEGA Retro|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140802133919/http://segaretro.org/Mission_Stick|archivedate=2014-08-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>、「雙搖桿控制器」（{{lang|ja|ツインスティック}}，HSS-0154）<ref name=":252" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/twin.html|script-title=ja:[セガハード大百科] ツインスティック|accessdate=2018-08-15|work=SEGA|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710143129/http://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/twin.html|archivedate=2016-07-10|dead-url=no|language=ja}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/Saturn_Twin-Stick|title=Saturn Twin-Stick - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-17|work=SEGA Retro|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171011065651/http://segaretro.org/Saturn_Twin-Stick|archivedate=2017-10-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>及「方向盤控制器」（{{lang|ja|レーシングコントローラ}}，HSS-0115/HSS-0141）<ref name=":252" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/racing.html|script-title=ja:[セガハード大百科] レーシングコントローラ|accessdate=2018-08-15|work=SEGA|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160924120531/http://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/racing.html|archivedate=2016-09-24|dead-url=no|language=ja}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://segaretro.org/Arcade_Racer_Joystick|title=Arcade Racer Joystick - Sega Retro|accessdate=2018-08-17|work=SEGA Retro|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171123132731/http://segaretro.org/Arcade_Racer_Joystick|archivedate=2017-11-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>等。因應多人對戰遊戲如《{{link-en|土星轟炸超人|Saturn Bomberman}}》，世嘉還推出了「6孔控制器擴充座」（{{lang|ja|マルチターミナル６}}，HSS-0103），並可同時使用兩個擴充座，使得同時遊玩人數增加到最多12人<ref name="EGM92">{{Cite magazine|title=Protos: Bomberman|magazine=[[Electronic_Gaming_Monthly|Electronic Gaming Monthly]]|issue=92|publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]]|date=1997-03|page=34|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Six Packed|date=1995-10|journal=[[GamePro|GamePro]]|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|IDG]]|issue=85|page=154|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/tarminal.html|script-title=ja:[セガハード大百科] マルチターミナル６|accessdate=2018-08-17|work=SEGA|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303232913/http://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/tarminal.html|archivedate=2016-03-03|dead-url=no|language=ja}}</ref>。

與前代家用遊戲機[[Mega_Drive|Mega Drive/SEGA Genesis]]的[[SEGA_Channel|SEGA Channel]]相同，世嘉也為世嘉土星提供了線上遊戲服務{{link-en|SEGANet|SegaNet}}。SEGANet透過使用卡帶擴充槽的[[數據機|數據機]]{{link-en|SEGA Net Link|Sega Net Link}}經[[撥號連線|撥接網路]]提供線上遊戲、閱讀電子郵件及瀏覽網路等服務<ref name="RetroinspectionSaturn" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/modem.html|script-title=ja:[セガハード大百科] セガサターンモデム|accessdate=2018-08-17|work=SEGA|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303225133/http://sega.jp/fb/segahard/ss/modem.html|archivedate=2016-03-03|dead-url=no|language=ja}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Internet Access, Network Games Hit Saturn - For Less than $400|last=|first=|date=1996-07|journal=[[Electronic_Gaming_Monthly|Electronic Gaming Monthly]]|publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]]|issue=84|page=18|language=en}}</ref>。由於SEGANet在官方鍵盤配件（{{lang|ja|セガサターンキーボード}}，HSS-0129/HSS-0159）發售前即上線，因此世嘉在SEGA Net Link的服務套件中附贈了內建上百個網址的光碟作為快捷連結，以供沒有鍵盤的使用者使用<ref>{{Cite news|title=Saturn to Get Internet Connection Facilities in '96!|date=1996-03|work=Sega Saturn Magazine|issue=5|volume=2|page=8|language=en}}</ref>。在世嘉土星快速地退出了家用遊戲機市場的情況之下，SEGA Net Link配件僅支援《[[DaytonaUSA|Daytona USA]]》、《{{link-en|世嘉冠軍拉力賽車|SEGA Rally Championship}}》、《[[毀滅公爵3D|毀滅公爵3D]]》、《{{link-en|土星轟炸超人|Saturn Bomberman}}》及《{{link-en|電腦戰機|Virtual On: Cyber Troopers}}》等五款遊戲{{sfn|Mott|2013|p=309}}<ref name="IGNSooth">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/05/20/sega-a-soothsayer-of-the-games-industry|title=SEGA: A Soothsayer of the Games Industry|language=en|accessdate=2018-09-17|author=Redsell, Adam|date=2012-05-20|work=IGN|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012022048/http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/05/20/sega-a-soothsayer-of-the-games-industry|archivedate=2013-10-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。世嘉甚至一度計畫開發內建數據機的世嘉土星機型，代號「世嘉冥王星」（SEGA Pluto），後因為世嘉土星生命週期過短而放棄研發<ref name=":10" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Is War Hell for Sega?|last=|first=|date=1996-01|journal={{link-en|Next Generation}}|publisher={{link-en|Imagine Media}}|issue=13|page=9|quote=Sega of Japan recently announced it was going to produce a Saturn with Internet access built in.|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2013/4/17/4237504/sega-pluto-prototype-console-surfaces-online|title=Forgotten Sega Pluto console prototype surfaces online|accessdate=2018-09-17|date=2013-04-17|last=Blagdon|first=Jeff|work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322090701/http://www.theverge.com/2013/4/17/4237504/sega-pluto-prototype-console-surfaces-online|archivedate=2014-03-22|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>。

== 遊戲陣容 ==
{{Main|世嘉土星遊戲列表}}
大多數世嘉土星的遊戲陣容皆為世嘉自家[[街機|街機]]遊戲的[[移植_(軟體)|移植]]版本，包括《[[DaytonaUSA|Daytona USA]]》、《{{link-en|世嘉冠軍拉力賽車|SEGA Rally Championship}}》、《{{link-en|電腦戰機|Virtual On: Cyber Troopers}}》、《{{link-en|死亡之屋|The House of the Dead (video game)}}》、《{{link-en|東京番外地|Last Bronx}}》、《[[VR戰警|VR戰警]]》系列及《[[VR战士系列|VR快打]]》系列等<ref name=":10" /><ref name="IGNHistory_pg6" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.allgame.com/game.php?id=15348&tab=review|title=The House of the Dead Review|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=|last=House|first=Michael L.|publisher=Allgame|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141114130911/http://www.allgame.com/game.php?id=15348&tab=review|archivedate=2014-11-14|dead-url=yes|language=en}}</ref><ref name=":12">{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/best-saturn-games-all-time/|title=Best Saturn games of all time|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=2014-03-06|publisher=GamesRadar|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408045155/http://www.gamesradar.com/best-saturn-games-all-time/|archivedate=2016-04-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>；[[卡普空|卡普空]]也為世嘉土星移植了許多[[格鬥遊戲|格鬥遊戲]]，包括《[[街头霸王ZERO_3|快打旋風ZERO 3]]》、《{{link-en|漫威超級英雄大戰快打旋風|Marvel Super Heroes vs. Street Fighter}}》及《{{link-en|魔域幽靈3|Darkstalkers 3}}》等，皆以其完整的原作還原度而聞名<ref name=":12" /><ref name=":11">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/top-25-consoles/18.html|title=SEGA Saturn is number 18|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=|publisher=IGN|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120120021737/http://www.ign.com/top-25-consoles/18.html|archivedate=2012-01-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外，世嘉土星也有許多優質的[[独占游戏|獨佔遊戲]]，包括《[[聖龍戰記|聖龍戰記]]》<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/saturn/197149-dragon-force/index.html|title=Dragon Force for Saturn|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=|publisher=GameRankings|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140326140418/http://www.gamerankings.com/saturn/197149-dragon-force/index.html|archivedate=2014-03-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>、《[[守護者列傳|守護者列傳]]》<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/saturn/573960-guardian-heroes/index.html|title=Guardian Heroes for Saturn|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=|publisher=GameRankings|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140326140810/http://www.gamerankings.com/saturn/573960-guardian-heroes/index.html|archivedate=2014-03-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{sfn|Mott|2013|page=300}}、《[[飛天幽夢|飛天幽夢]]》<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/saturn/198201-nights-into-dreams/index.html|title=Nights Into Dreams for Saturn|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=|publisher=GameRankings|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304110105/http://www.gamerankings.com/saturn/198201-nights-into-dreams/index.html|archivedate=2016-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{sfn|Mott|2013|p=302}}、《[[光明與黑暗III|光明與黑暗III]]》<ref name=":10" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/saturn/198623-shining-force-iii/index.html|title=Shining Force III for Saturn|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=|publisher=GameRankings|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140326135954/http://www.gamerankings.com/saturn/198623-shining-force-iii/index.html|archivedate=2014-03-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Power Profiles: Takahashi Brothers|date=2008-08|journal=Nintendo Power|issue=229|volume=21|pages=80–83}}</ref>{{sfn|Mott|2013|p=350}}、《[[铁甲飞龙_RPG|飛龍騎士RPG]]》<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/saturn/198258-panzer-dragoon-saga/index.html|title=Panzer Dragoon Saga for Saturn|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=|publisher=GameRankings|language=en|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6DXsyRMIa?url=http://www.gamerankings.com/saturn/198258-panzer-dragoon-saga/index.html|archivedate=2013-01-09|dead-url=no}} cf.{{Cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/cgi-bin/review.cgi?sys=sat&path=may98&doc=pds|title=Panzer Dragoon Saga|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=1998-05-15|work=|publisher=Game Informer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19990824121149/http://www.gameinformer.com/cgi-bin/review.cgi?sys=sat&path=may98&doc=pds|archivedate=1999-08-24|quote=Only [[Final_Fantasy_VII|Final Fantasy VII]] tops it.|language=en|dead-url=yes}} cf. {{Cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/reviews/panzer-dragoon-saga/|title=Panzer Dragoon Saga Review|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=1998-03-25|publisher=Edge|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141224050513/http://www.edge-online.com/reviews/panzer-dragoon-saga/|archivedate=2014-12-24|quote=Adds a creative depth only SquareSoft games can currently rival.|dead-url=yes|language=en}} cf. {{Cite web|url=http://www.next-generation.com/jsmid/reviews/1788.html|title=Panzer Dragoon Saga|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=1998-05-14|publisher=Next Generation|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19990829131749/http://www.next-generation.com/jsmid/reviews/1788.html|archivedate=1999-08-29|quote=One of the best RPGs ever.|dead-url=yes|language=en}}</ref>及《[[铁甲飞龙|飛龍騎士]]》系列等<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/saturn/562829-panzer-dragoon-ii-zwei/index.html|title=Panzer Dragoon II Zwei for Saturn|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=|publisher=GameRankings|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140326135417/http://www.gamerankings.com/saturn/562829-panzer-dragoon-ii-zwei/index.html|archivedate=2014-03-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>；部分[[PlayStation_(遊戲機)|PlayStation]]遊戲如《[[惡魔城X_月下夜想曲|惡魔城X 月下夜想曲]]》、《[[生化危機_(1996年遊戲)|惡靈古堡]]》及《[[反重力賽車2097|磁浮飛車2097]]》等也有移植至世嘉土星，不過品質良莠不齊<ref name=":12" />。由{{link-en|Lobotomy Software|Lobotomy Software}}開發的3D遊戲《{{link-en|PowerSlave|}}》有效的將世嘉土星的3D運算能力運用至極，以致於連世嘉官方也請求他們協助開發《[[毀滅公爵3D|毀滅公爵3D]]》及《[[雷神之锤_(游戏)|雷神之鎚]]》的世嘉土星移植版本<ref name="1UP Pleasure and Pain" /><ref name=":12" />；在知名[[體育遊戲|體育遊戲]]開發商[[艺电|藝電]]倒戈至PlayStation陣營，加上世嘉本家為世嘉土星開發的體育遊戲並不多的情況之下<ref name="1UP Pleasure and Pain" /><ref name="IGNHistory_pg6" />{{sfn|Kent|2001|p=533}}，世嘉土星在體育遊戲陣容方面一直是大幅落後於PlayStation陣營的，不過還是有《{{link-en|棒球世界大賽|World Series Baseball (video game)}}》及《{{link-en|世嘉世界足球|SEGA Worldwide Soccer}}》系列等優質作品<ref name="1UP Pleasure and Pain" /><ref>cf. {{Cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/cgi-bin/review.cgi?sys=sat&path=nov95&doc=series|title=Sega Sports Does It One More Time|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=1995-11|publisher=Game Informer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19990824140309/http://www.gameinformer.com/cgi-bin/review.cgi?sys=sat&path=nov95&doc=series|archivedate=1999-08-24|language=en|dead-url=no}} cf. {{Cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/cgi-bin/review.cgi?sys=sat&path=jan98&doc=wws|title=Worldwide Soccer '98|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=1998-01|publisher=Game Informer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19990930170004/http://www.gameinformer.com/cgi-bin/review.cgi?sys=sat&path=jan98&doc=wws|archivedate=1999-09-30|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除此之外，由於平臺開放的電子遊戲分級中曾出現在家用遊戲機業界中極為罕見的「[[十八禁|X指定]]」分級（相當於現今的[[CERO_Z|CERO Z]]分級，於1996年廢止並改制為「18歲以上推獎」分級，相當於現今的[[CERO_D|CERO D]]分級），因此世嘉土星上也出現了一些其他電子遊戲機平臺上很難看到的[[美少女遊戲|美少女遊戲]]以及[[日本成人遊戲|成人遊戲]]，如《{{link-ja|野野村醫院|野々村病院の人々}}》及《{{link-ja|超級真實麻將PV|スーパーリアル麻雀#スーパーリアル麻雀PV}}》等<ref name=":10" /><ref>{{Cite web|script-title=ja:セガサターン１８禁（Ｘ指定）ソフト|url=http://www.retrogame-labo.com/repo/repo14.html|work=レトロゲームラボ|accessdate=2019-04-29|language=ja|title=|author=|date=|publisher=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170613045458/http://www.retrogame-labo.com/repo/repo14.html|archivedate=2017-06-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://imgcc.naver.jp/kaze/mission/USER/20180220/71/7605171/13/1173x1497xf3700998e70f2d4e06538f.jpg|title=|accessdate=|author=|date=1997-05-04|publisher=Fami通|script-title=ja:ファミ通 人気ギャルゲー TOP50|archive-date=2021-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210623070449/http://imgcc.naver.jp/kaze/mission/USER/20180220/71/7605171/13/1173x1497xf3700998e70f2d4e06538f.jpg}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=|url=https://nlab.itmedia.co.jp/nl/articles/1710/05/news015.html|work=ねとらぼ|accessdate=2019-04-29|language=ja|author=|date=2017-10-05|publisher=|script-title=ja:もし「ミニセガサターン」が発売したら収録されていて欲しい名作美少女ゲー10選|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190405022203/https://nlab.itmedia.co.jp/nl/articles/1710/05/news015.html|archivedate=2019-04-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據世嘉官方統計，官方授權的世嘉土星遊戲陣容約600款，是[[任天堂64|任天堂64]]遊戲陣容的2倍之多<ref name=":17">{{Cite web|url=http://www.usgamer.net/articles/the-lost-child-of-a-house-divided-a-sega-saturn-retrospective|title=The Lost Child of a House Divided: A Sega Saturn Retrospective|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=2014-11-17|language=en|last=Parish|first=Jeremy|publisher=USgamer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141215095100/http://www.usgamer.net/articles/the-lost-child-of-a-house-divided-a-sega-saturn-retrospective|archivedate=2014-12-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sega.jp/history/hard/segasaturn/software.html|script-title=ja:セガハード大百科 - セガサターン専用ソフトの一覧|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=|work=セガハード大百科|publisher=SEGA|language=ja|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180808233747/https://sega.jp/history/hard/segasaturn/software.html|archivedate=2018-08-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[File:Virtua_Cop_Gameplay.jpg|替代=]]》的遊戲截圖]]
由於《{{link-en|音速小子X-Treme|Sonic X-Treme}}》於1997年初中止開發的關係<ref name="Edge X-Treme" /><ref name="Fahs revisited" /><ref name="Xtreme" />，導致世嘉土星上沒有任何獨佔的《[[音速小子系列|音速小子]]》系列遊戲，不過仍有如《[[音速小子R|音速小子R]]》、《{{link-en|音速小子3D|Sonic 3D Blast}}》及《{{link-en|音速小子嘉年華|Sonic Jam}}》等衍生遊戲及合輯發行<ref name="RetroinspectionSaturn" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/jan97/sonic.html|title=Sonic 3D Blast|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=1997-01|publisher=Game Informer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19971021144336/http://www.gameinformer.com/jan97/sonic.html|archivedate=1997-10-21|dead-url=yes|language=en}}</ref>。世嘉企圖以全新3D遊戲《{{link-en|Bug！|Bug!}}》填補空缺，不過遊戲評價兩極<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/saturn/573934-bug/index.html|title=Bug! for Saturn|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=|publisher=GameRankings|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140315201655/http://www.gamerankings.com/saturn/573934-bug/index.html|archivedate=2014-03-15|dead-url=no}} cf. {{Cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/sep95/bug.html|title=Not To Be Denied!|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=1995-09|last=McNamara|first=Andy|publisher=Game Informer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19971120012847/http://www.gameinformer.com/sep95/bug.html|archivedate=1997-11-20|dead-url=yes|language=en}} cf. {{Cite journal|title=Bug! (review)|author=|url=|date=1995-08|journal=Electronic Gaming Monthly|issue=73|doi=|others=|year=|volume=7|page=38|pmid=|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/02/02/what-hath-sonic-wrought-vol-10|title=What Hath Sonic Wrought? Vol. 10|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=2009-02-02|last=Buchanan|first=Levi|publisher=IGN|quote='''[[Steven_Spielberg|Steven Spielberg]], CES 1995:''' This is the character! This is the character that is going to do it for Saturn!|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111082707/http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/02/02/what-hath-sonic-wrought-vol-10|archivedate=2013-11-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Bug!|author=|url=|date=1995-09|journal=Next Generation|issue=9|doi=|others=|year=|volume=1|page=|pages=88–89|pmid=|language=en}}</ref>。此外，由世嘉開發團隊[[Sonic_Team|Sonic Team]]推出的《飛天幽夢》，被視為是世嘉土星上最引人注目的3D遊戲之一；雖然不像[[任天堂|任天堂]]的《[[超級瑪利歐64|超級瑪利歐64]]》一樣屬於全3D環境，但《飛天幽夢》以其不受拘束的角色移動方式及獨特的操作系统，向業界展示了[[類比搖桿|類比搖桿]]及3D遊戲的潛力<ref name=":10" /><ref name="Edge Nights">{{Cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/reviews/nights-dreams-review/|title=Nights into Dreams (review)|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=1996-08-02|publisher=Edge|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141224050554/http://www.edge-online.com/reviews/nights-dreams-review/|archivedate=2014-12-24|dead-url=yes|language=en}} cf. {{Cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/nights-dreams-retrospective/|title=Nights Into Dreams Retrospective|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=June 8, 2007|publisher=Edge|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141031062946/http://www.edge-online.com/features/nights-dreams-retrospective/|archivedate=2014-10-31|dead-url=yes|language=en}} cf. {{Cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/retrospective-nights-into-dreams/|title=Retrospective: Nights Into Dreams|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=2014-03-15|publisher=Edge|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006070937/http://www.edge-online.com/features/retrospective-nights-into-dreams/|archivedate=2014-10-06|quote=The 3D environments were drawn by one processor, while another handled the 2D enemies, hoops and trees, melding them seamlessly to create a smooth, surprisingly fast-moving game that still looks striking today.|dead-url=yes|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/08/18/nights-into-dreams-retro-review|title=Nights into Dreams Retro Review|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=2008-08-18|last=Buchanan|first=Levi|publisher=IGN|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121227002758/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/08/18/nights-into-dreams-retro-review|archivedate=2012-12-27|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Robinson">{{Cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-10-05-nights-into-dreams-hd-review|title=Nights Into Dreams HD review|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=2012-05-10|last=Robinson|first=Martin|publisher=Eurogamer|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102234514/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-10-05-nights-into-dreams-hd-review|archivedate=2012-11-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>；另外一款由Sonic Team於世嘉土星生命週期後期推出的3D動作遊戲《{{link-en|烈火英豪|Burning Rangers}}》，則以其純熟的硬體[[半透明|半透明]]色運算技術運用而聞名<ref name=":10" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Classic Reviews: Burning Rangers|author=|url=|date=2002-06|journal=Game Informer|issue=110|doi=|others=|year=|volume=12|page=104|pmid=|quote=This futuristic fire-fighting game was an instant cult classic ... The game has all the makings of a masterpiece, but is held back by both the Saturn's limited power and the fireman motif.|language=en}}</ref><ref name="IGN BR">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/09/03/burning-rangers-retro-review|title=Burning Rangers Retro Review|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=2008-09-03|last=Buchanan|first=Levi|publisher=IGN|quote=A wholly competent (but somewhat workmanlike, as the Saturn was not as good at 3D as the PSone or N64) action-adventure game.|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129043357/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/09/03/burning-rangers-retro-review|archivedate=2014-11-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{sfn|Mott|2013|p=353}}。

在美國世嘉的戰略規劃限制之下，有許多於日本聞名或銷量極佳的遊戲（如《[[櫻花大戰系列|櫻花大戰]]》系列等）皆從未在海外被翻譯或發行<ref name="1UP Pleasure and Pain" /><ref name="IGNHistory_pg6" /><ref>cf. {{Cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/japan-votes-all-time-top-100/|title=Japan Votes on All Time Top 100|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=2006-03-03|publisher=Edge|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141010035551/http://www.edge-online.com/features/japan-votes-all-time-top-100/|archivedate=2014-10-10|dead-url=yes|language=en}}</ref>；其他如《[[冒險奇譚_(遊戲)|冒險奇譚]]》、《[[露娜_銀河之星物語|露娜 銀河之星物語]]》及《[[生死格鬥|生死格鬥]]》等遊戲雖然最初有發行在世嘉土星上，但是在日本以外地區卻只有[[PlayStation_(遊戲機)|PlayStation]]版本獲得翻譯<ref name="1UP Pleasure and Pain" /><ref name=":12" /><ref>cf. {{Cite journal|title=Catching up with Tecmo's Prince of Darkness|author=|url=|date=2004-12|journal=Game Informer|issue=140|doi=|others=|year=|volume=15|page=203|pmid=|quote='''{{link-en|Tomonobu Itagaki}}:''' Saturn was a great machine, great system. If someone were to ask me if I want to make a game for PSone or Saturn I would—100 percent of the time—make games for the Saturn.|language=en}}</ref>。許多優質的遊戲因此而被埋沒，例如於1998年1月於日本首發的《[[铁甲飞龙_RPG|飛龍騎士RPG]]》雖然被稱為世嘉土星上最優秀的[[角色扮演遊戲|角色扮演遊戲]]，卻在世嘉土星的衰頹及美國世嘉的戰略規劃限制之下無法在海外大量發行，後來輿論甚至稱此舉為「（世嘉土星）恥辱的終沒」（"ignominious send-off"）<ref name="IGN BR" /><ref name="Sad Tale">{{Cite journal|title=Panzer Dragoon Saga: The Sad Tale of the Saturn's Last Great Game|author=|url=|date=2007-12|journal=Game Informer|issue=176|doi=|others=|year=|volume=17|page=|pages=164–165|pmid=|quote=One of the greatest games ever crafted by human hands ... Critically, the game was a smash hit, lauded as one of the year's best, and generally considered the Saturn's finest title. But despite glowing reviews across the board, Saga was destined to fail. Sega had moved on—shifted its focus to developing its next console, the Dreamcast, and wasn't willing to risk any more money on a system that had already lost so much. Therefore, less than 20,000 retail copies of Panzer Dragoon Saga were even made, making it a very rare title and a prize for collectors.|language=en}}</ref>{{sfn|Mott|2013|p=361}}；在《光明與黑暗III》三部作品中，也只有一款遊戲在海外獲得翻譯並成功發行{{sfn|Mott|2013|p=350}}。同時，世嘉也因低估了許多前代主機[[Mega_Drive|Mega Drive/SEGA Genesis]]平臺遊戲作品的[[智慧財產權|角色版權]]潛力而受到抨擊，其中又以《{{link-en|武士道之王|Eternal Champions}}》系列第三作的開發爭議最大<ref name="1UP Pleasure and Pain" /><ref name=":17" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/vgs/sat/segafight/page11.html|title=The History of Sega Fighting Games|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=|publisher=GameSpot|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090517063548/http://www.gamespot.com/features/vgs/sat/segafight/page11.html|archivedate=2009-05-17|page=11|dead-url=yes|language=en}} cf. {{Cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/vgs/sat/segafight/page12.html|title=The History of Sega Fighting Games|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=|work=GameSpot|publisher=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090517061825/http://www.gamespot.com/features/vgs/sat/segafight/page12.html|archivedate=2009-05-17|page=12|dead-url=yes|language=en}}</ref>。

由於世嘉土星快速地退出了家用遊戲機市場，加上世嘉土星本身的硬體機能限制，導致《[[音速小子大冒險|音速小子大冒險]]》、《[[莎木_一章_橫須賀|莎木]]》、《[[VR快打3|VR快打3]]》及《[[惡靈古堡2|惡靈古堡2]]》等知名遊戲的預定發行平臺最後皆轉移至世嘉土星的後繼主機[[Dreamcast|Dreamcast]]，甚至直接付諸流水<ref name="IGN Shenmue" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/re2-for-saturn-canceled/1100-2465273/|title=RE2 for Saturn Canceled|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=1998-10-21|last=Ohbuchi|first=Yutaka|publisher=GameSpot|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110081451/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/re2-for-saturn-canceled/1100-2465273/|archivedate=2014-11-10|dead-url=yes|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.next-generation.com/news/112296b.shtml|title=Suzuki: Yes on VF3|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=1996-11-22|publisher=Next Generation|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19961220182051/http://www.next-generation.com/news/112296b.shtml|archivedate=1996-12-20|dead-url=yes|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/vgs/sat/segafight/page18.html|title=The History of Sega Fighting Games, Page 18|accessdate=2018-08-21|author=|date=|publisher=GameSpot|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090517084728/http://www.gamespot.com/features/vgs/sat/segafight/page18.html|archivedate=2009-05-17|quote=Sega executives started to quietly state that Virtua Fighter 3 was not going to come out for the Saturn.|dead-url=yes|language=en}}</ref>。
{{Clear}}

== 評價與影響 ==
日本電子遊戲雜誌《[[Famicom通訊|Famicom通訊]]》（現《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》）給世嘉土星打出了24分（滿分40分）的分數，優於PlayStation的19分<ref>{{Cite magazine|script-title=ja:セガサターン|magazine=週刊ファミコン通信|issue=335|page=166|date=1995-05-19|language=ja}}</ref>。1995年6月，《[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]》與《[[娛樂週刊|娛樂週刊]]》皆評價世嘉土星為當時市面上最強大的家用遊戲機，前者讚譽其光碟機的效能及音效表現，後者則稱《[[飛龍騎士_(電子遊戲)|飛龍騎士]]》「戲劇張力十足、史詩級刺激」，並解析了世嘉土星「足以改變產業生態」的硬體機能<ref>{{Cite web|last=Lynch|first=Dennis|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1995-06-16/entertainment/9506160099_1_sega-saturn-saturn-system-32x|title=Saturn Runs Rings Around Its Rivals|work=Chicago Tribune|date=1995-06-16|accessdate=2015-01-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150120044130/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1995-06-16/entertainment/9506160099_1_sega-saturn-saturn-system-32x|archivedate=2015-01-20|dead-url=no|author=|publisher=|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Kim|first=Albert|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,297526,00.html|title=Sega Saturn|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=1995-06-09|accessdate=2015-01-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150120053245/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,297526,00.html|archivedate=2015-01-20|dead-url=no|author=|publisher=|language=en}}</ref>。1995年12月，《Next Generation》給予世嘉土星三顆半星（滿分五顆星）的成績，認為世嘉的市場行銷策略及堅實的街機遊戲陣容基礎將為世嘉土星帶來優勢，不過同時也批評主機過於複雜的硬體架構<ref name="NextGenDec" />。《[[電子遊戲月刊|電子遊戲月刊]]》的四位評論者於1996年12月出版的消費者購買指南中分別給出8、6、7及8分（滿分10分）的成績，低於PlayStation的9、10、10及9分<ref>{{Cite journal|title=EGM rates the systems of 1996!|author=|url=|date=1996-12|journal=1996 Video Game Buyer's Guide|issue=|doi=|others=|year=|volume=|page=|language=en|pmid=}}</ref>；至1998年時開始出現以貧乏、素質不穩定的遊戲陣容批評世嘉土星的評論。評論者克里斯平·博耶（Crispin Boyer）表示：「（世嘉）土星是唯一一部能讓我這個月給出正面評價，下個月又給出負面評價的電子遊戲機。」<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Electronic Gaming Monthly looks at the top systems for this year|author=|url=|date=1998-12|journal=1998 Video Game Buyer's Guide|issue=|doi=|others=|year=|volume=|page=51|language=en|pmid=}}</ref>

輿論對世嘉土星的評價褒貶不一，不過對其整體遊戲陣容多抱持正面評價<ref name="IGNHistory_pg6" /><ref name=":12" />。[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]的格雷格·塞瓦特（Greg Sewart）認為：「（世嘉）土星將以史上問題最多，但也是最好的電子遊戲機之一之名留名青史。」<ref name="1UP Pleasure and Pain" />[[IGN|IGN]]於2009年將世嘉土星列為「史上最好的電子遊戲機」名單中的第18名，報導中表示：「儘管（世嘉）土星在市場中無法與索尼和任天堂家用遊戲機競爭，但《飛天幽夢》、《VR快打》系列與《飛龍騎士》系列等獨佔遊戲使其成為玩家最鍾愛的主機平臺之一。」<ref name=":11" />《[[Edge_(雜誌)|Edge]]》並提到：「死忠的支持者將銘記這部為他們帶來《烈火英豪》、《守護者列傳》、《聖龍戰記》和《鐵甲飛龍 RPG》的電子遊戲機。」<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/how-consoles-die/3/|title=How Consoles Die|page=3|work=Edge|date=2008-09-17|accessdate=2015-03-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129171554/http://www.edge-online.com/features/how-consoles-die/3/|archivedate=2014-11-29|author=|publisher=|language=en}}</ref>2015年，《[[衛報|衛報]]》的基思斯·圖爾特（Keith Stuart）在報導中表示：「（世嘉）土星或許擁有史上最強大的2D射擊遊戲及格鬥遊戲陣容。」<ref>{{Cite web|last=Stuart|first=Keith|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/may/15/sega-saturn-how-to-buy|title=Sega Saturn – how to buy one and what to play|work=The Guardian|date=2015-05-15|accessdate=2015-05-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150526192113/http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/may/15/sega-saturn-how-to-buy|archivedate=2015-05-26|dead-url=no|author=|publisher=}}</ref>《[[Retro_Gamer|Retro Gamer]]》的達米安·麥克費蘭（Damien McFerran）表示：「即使（世嘉）土星平臺上的多數遊戲已經於其他平臺發行移植版或續作，但直到今日它仍因為特立獨行的軟硬體設計風格而十分熱門。」<ref name="RetroinspectionSaturn" />IGN的亞當·雷塞爾（Adam Redsell）表示：「世嘉在（世嘉）土星及Dreamcast時代裡那種吊兒啷噹（"devil-may-care"）的開發風格今日在[[獨立遊戲|獨立遊戲]]開發商以外已經很難看到了。」<ref name="IGNSooth" />據Necrosoft Games製作人{{link-en|布蘭登·謝菲爾德|Brandon Sheffield}}表示，「（世嘉）土星是那些由於過於『成人』而無法在其他平臺上發行的遊戲的理想去處（尤其在日本，世嘉土星是唯一允許限制級遊戲上架的主機平臺），並進一步推動了業界的發展。」<ref name=":17" />塞瓦特對世嘉土星的第一方遊戲陣容有著極好的評價，並在報導中讚譽了Sonic Team的創造力以及AM2諸多優質的街機移植作品，以及日本地區限定的作品如何造就北美遊戲進口市場的繁榮<ref name="1UP Pleasure and Pain" />；IGN的特拉維斯·法赫斯（Travis Fahs）則批評世嘉土星遊戲陣容不足，以及相較於Dreamcast在遊戲陣容的創新程度方面顯得弱勢<ref name="IGN History of Dreamcast" />。

另一方面，輿論多批評世嘉在決策上的諸多錯誤。麥克費蘭抨擊了世嘉在世嘉土星開發期間的商業布局，認為世嘉「對消費者及業界的了解不足」<ref name="RetroinspectionSaturn" />；同時，世嘉土星生命週期後期的主要負責人之一斯托拉爾因主張放棄世嘉土星而遭到批評<ref name="1UP Pleasure and Pain" />。據法赫斯表示：「斯托拉爾的決定被很多世嘉的粉絲批評，對他們來說他就像惡魔一般；但是或許暫時重整勢力比傷痕累累的進行下一場戰鬥好上許多，畢竟他的確在Dreamcast開發及先行宣傳期間稱職地完成了工作。」<ref name="IGNHistory_pg6" />斯托拉爾本人也為此辯護：「我認為（世嘉）土星對公司的害處遠大於益處。我不想打一場不會贏的戰爭。」{{sfn|Kent|2001|p=558}}謝菲爾德認為，世嘉土星採用以四邊形（而非三角形）為基礎的多邊形建構技術間接地使第三方廠商的軟體支援減少許多，但同時也表示「要是世嘉土星成為當代最主流的電子遊戲機的話，或許往後業界的標準規格就不會是三角形多邊形而是四邊形多邊形了。」<ref name=":17" />前{{link-en|Working Designs}}社長維克多·艾爾蘭（Victor Ireland）則認為世嘉土星是「遊戲業界未來的起始點」，因為其雙中央處理器硬體架構使開發者首次跳脫出單核運算的硬體，開始以多工處理為基礎開發作品<ref name="1UP Pleasure and Pain" />。此外，[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]（現[[GamesRadar+|GamesRadar+]]）的賈斯汀·多維爾（Justin Towell）在報導中讚譽了世嘉土星的3D控制器：「（世嘉）土星的3D控制器奠定了往後大多數電子遊戲機控制器皆採用的類比肩鍵以及左搖桿設置；倒是那什麼三柄控制器（"three-pronged controller"，即世嘉土星競爭對手[[任天堂64|任天堂64]]附設的控制器外型）設計我近年來可從沒看過有哪家廠商採用呢。」<ref>{{Cite web|last=Towell|first=Justin|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/sega-saturn-turns-20-its-not-shit-as-you-think/|title=Sega Saturn turns 20, and it's not as shit as you think|work=GamesRadar|date=2014-11-22|accessdate=2015-01-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150120044933/http://www.gamesradar.com/sega-saturn-turns-20-its-not-shit-as-you-think/|archivedate=2015-01-20|dead-url=no|author=|publisher=|language=en}}</ref>

[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]的道格拉斯·C·佩里（Douglass C. Perry）表示由於世嘉土星在北美地區的突然發售以及伴隨而來的遊戲陣容空窗期，使許多玩家「感覺被世嘉潑了冷水」<ref>{{Cite web|author=Perry, Douglass C.|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/4128/the_rise_and_fall_of_the_dreamcast.php|title=The Rise and Fall of Dreamcast|work=Gamasutra|date=2009-09-09|accessdate=2014-12-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140318193258/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/4128/the_rise_and_fall_of_the_dreamcast.php|archivedate=2014-03-18|dead-url=no|publisher=|language=en}}</ref>。塞瓦特以及IGN的列維·布坎南（Levi Buchanan）認為世嘉土星的失敗是世嘉退出電子遊戲機硬體市場的主要因素，但USgamer（[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]支部）的傑里米·帕里許（Jeremy Parish）認為世嘉土星僅僅是世嘉衰敗的症狀而已，真正的根源在於Mega Drive/SEGA Genesis時代過多的配件分散了市場，以及日本世嘉與美國世嘉的惡性競爭等因素<ref name="1UP Pleasure and Pain" /><ref name=":17" /><ref name="Top 10">{{Cite web|last=Buchanan|first=Levi|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/07/29/top-10-sega-saturn-games|title=Top 10 SEGA Saturn Games|work=IGN|date=2008-07-29|accessdate=2014-03-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170712125018/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/07/29/top-10-sega-saturn-games|archivedate=2017-07-12|dead-url=no|author=|publisher=|language=en}}</ref>。謝菲爾德認為世嘉土星的失敗象徵了日本電子遊戲產業的衰頹：「世嘉自認是無敵的，認為當前的組織結構和地區資源分配能讓她存活下來；然而事實上，讓企業組織更加靈活，並尋求西方世界的協助與配合更有機會解除公司的困境。」<ref name=":17" />斯圖爾特認為世嘉「沒有察覺電子遊戲產業正在進步，意即業界趨勢自傳統的街機遊戲和角色扮演遊戲領域，逐漸轉移至以主機研發社群為基礎，對遊戲結構及遊戲性進行的革新。」Pulp365的評論者馬特·帕德羅基（Matt Paprocki）說道，「（世嘉）土星是一次失敗的嘗試，她凸顯了現實的殘酷，但同時也是一個重要的里程碑。請銘記她帶給了我們什麼。」<ref name=":17" />

